web/20131231143637/http://books.google.com/books?id=2GZ7N4wOeGYC&pg=PA207 | archive-date = 2013-12-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。相反，交配更經常地指非人動物的交媾過程；它可代表異性或{{link-en|同性配偶|Same-sex relationship}}間的任何性活動<ref name="Barrows">{{cite book | author = Edward M. Barrows | title = Animal Behavior Desk Reference: A Dictionary of Animal Behavior, Ecology, and Evolution | publisher = Taylor & Francis | year = 2011 | pages = 122–124 | accessdate = 2013-08-25 | isbn = 1439836515 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=2vf7ZbLENzEC&pg=PA122 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143604/http://books.google.com/books?id=2vf7ZbLENzEC&pg=PA122 | archive-date = 2013-12-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但一般定義為一種把精子從雄性體內轉移到雌性體內的性生殖行為，或雄性和雌性之間的有性生殖行為<ref name="Barrows"/><ref name="Copulation1">{{cite web|title=Copulation|publisher=Dorland's Medical Dictionary for Health Consumers, 2007/TheFreeDictionary.com for various dictionary definitions|accessdate=2012-09-06|url=http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/copulation|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20120810012929/http://medical-dictionary.thefreedictionary.com/copulation|archive-date=2012-08-10|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Copulation2">{{cite web|title=Copulation|publisher=The American Heritage Dictionary of the English Language, Fifth Edition|year=2011|accessdate=2013-08-23|url=http://ahdictionary.com/word/search.html?q=Copulation|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131013144535/http://ahdictionary.com/word/search.html?q=Copulation|archive-date=2013-10-13|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

