l = https://web.archive.org/web/20140108013209/http://books.google.com/books?id=FZOjc8ouMlsC&pg=PA259 | archive-date = 2014-01-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Miller">{{cite book | title = Perspectives on Evil and Violence | publisher = Psychology Press | year = 1999 | page = 240 | accessdate = 2013-04-29 | isbn = 0805897844 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=WLn50MYFfqcC&pg=PA240 | quote = Many people consider penile–vaginal intercourse the only form of 'real' sex. | author = Arthur G. Miller | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20140108012849/http://books.google.com/books?id=WLn50MYFfqcC&pg=PA240 | archive-date = 2014-01-08 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Kalbfleisch">{{cite book | title = Gender Power and Communication in Human Relationships | publisher = [[Routledge|Routledge]] | year = 2012 | page = 153 | accessdate = 2013-04-30 | isbn = 1136480501 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=LyMo1RUJwj0C&pg=PA153 | author1 = Pamela J. Kalbfleisch | author2 = Michael J. Cody | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905090514/https://books.google.com/books?id=LyMo1RUJwj0C&pg=PA153 | archive-date = 2015-09-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在概念上把性愛與陰道交混为一谈此一點，可能会削弱了[[非異性戀|非異性戀者]]獲得性功能障礙及可能從事之性行為的信息的真偽性，異性戀者可能從事的非陰道性活動的信息亦同樣如是，其真偽性亦都可能因此而削弱<ref name=" Baum"/>。

研究發現性交的定義有時是有爭議的。1999年一項由[[金賽研究所|金賽研究所]]進行的研究中，先在美國29個州份隨機地取得599个大學生樣本，其後對他們進行訪談。结果發現「所有大學生受訪者都認為陰莖－陰道交是一種性愛活動」，19-20%認為肛交不是一種性愛活動（sex），還有60%的受訪者認為口部－生殖器（[[咂陽|咂陽]]、[[舐陰|舐陰]]）接觸不能算作有過性關係（have sex）<ref name="Cox"/><ref name="Kauth">{{cite book | title = True Nature: A Theory of Sexual Attraction | publisher = Springer | year = 2000 | page = 74 | accessdate = 2012-08-30 | isbn = 0306463903 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=PzDKr-qCdTAC&pg=PA74 | author = Michael R Kauth | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143915/http://books.google.com/books?id=PzDKr-qCdTAC&pg=PA74 | archive-date = 2013-12-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Jayson">{{cite news |first=Sharon |last=Jayson |title='Technical virginity' becomes part of teens' equation |publisher=''[[USA_Today|USA Today]]'' |date=2005-10-19 |accessdate=2009-08-07 |url=http://www.usatoday.com/news/health/2005-10-19-teens-technical-virginity_x.htm |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305090437/http://usatoday30.usatoday.com/news/health/2005-10-19-teens-technical-virginity_x.htm |archivedate=2016-03-05 }}</ref>。一項在2003年發表於《[[加拿大性學期刊|加拿大性學期刊]]》的研究則同樣地聚焦於來自美國、英國和澳大利亞等地的大學生對「有過性關係」的定義，「在這三地的研究中，絕大多數受訪者（超過97％）都把陰莖－陰道交包括在『有過性關係』的定義中，認為陰莖－肛交是有過性關係者則較少有（70％至90％之間）……把口部－生殖器行为定為有過性關係的受訪者约有32％至58％」<ref name="Randall"/>[[美国疾病控制与预防中心|美国疾病控制与预防中心]]（CDC）在2009年指出：「儘管青少年從事口交的頻率及有從事者的人數有限，但有些數據表明，許多從事口交的青少年不認為那是『有過性關係』。因此，他們可能會以口交為體驗性行為的一种選擇，但在心中認為自己仍是在禁欲<ref name="CDC, oral sex">{{cite web |title=Oral Sex and HIV Risk |date=2009-06 |accessdate=2013-08-30 |publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC) |url=http://www.cdc.gov/hiv/resources/Factsheets/pdf/oralsex.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120119061226/http://www.cdc.gov/hiv/resources/Factsheets/pdf/oralsex.pdf |archivedate=2012-01-19 }}</ref>。」

性活動研究的問題具体性還可影響受訪者對性交或其他性行為的定義。金賽研究所的另一項研究則訪問484個年齡介乎18-96歲之樣本。結果顯示將近95%的受訪者同意「陰莖－陰道交就是『有過性關係』，但当問題變得更为具体时，此數值就有了變化。」11%的受訪者以有没達至[[性高潮|高潮]]去定義有過性關係與否，認為不存在性高潮即表示没「有過性關係」。「大約80%的受訪者認为陰莖-肛交亦等同『有過性關係』，約70%則認為口交等同『有過性關係』 。」<ref name="Cox"/>有沒有使用[[避孕套|避孕套]]也是一個影響因子，一些人認為有避孕套保護的性行為不是「真正的性行為」<ref name="Cox"/><ref name="Engel">{{cite book | author = Jonathan Engel | title = The Epidemic: A History of Aids | publisher = [[HarperCollins|HarperCollins]] | year = 2009 | page = 242 | accessdate = 2013-08-30 | isbn = 0061856762 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=GQud7Hf6oLIC&pg=PT242 | quote = Many men simply did not like the feel of condoms, or associated them with emasculation. They say, 'Unless it's flesh on flesh, it's not real sex... | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143538/http://books.google.com/books?id=GQud7Hf6oLIC&pg=PT242 | archive-date = 2013-12-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Wekwete">{{cite book | author = Naomi N. Wekwete | title = Adolescent Pregnancy Challenges in the Era of HIV and AIDS: A Case Study of a Selected Rural Area in Zimbabwe | publisher = African Books Collective | year = 2010 | page = 49 | accessdate = 2013-08-30 | isbn = 9994455486 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=LB45dcqSOpsC&pg=PA49 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143622/http://books.google.com/books?id=LB45dcqSOpsC&pg=PA49 | archive-date = 2013-12-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一項研究報告指出，年齡較大的男性（65歲或以上）更為傾向不把有避孕套保護的性活動視為真正的性行為<ref name="Cox"/>。此一觀点在非洲男性間十分普遍<ref name="Engel"/><ref name="Wekwete"/>，在該地涉及避孕套保護的性活動通常與完全的去勢有關，因為避孕套可防止直接的生殖器接觸<ref name="Engel"/>。

==有关表現及行为==
{{See also|人类性行为|人类的性}}
===感情纽带===
從純生殖活動到情感結合，性交起到廣泛作用。性交和性活動通常在人類的[[感情纽带|感情纽带]]中扮演着十分重要的角色<ref name="Diamond"/>。性行為本身亦有加強感情纽带和與伴侣一同享樂的功用<ref name="Diamond"/>。

對於人類及[[倭黑猩猩|倭黑猩猩]]而言，雌性的排卵相對較為{{link-en|隱蔽|concealed ovulation}}，所以不論雌性自身抑或其伴侣，通常都不知道雌性一方在某個時刻会否受孕。這種独特的生物特徵之所以出現，可能是因为能够在性伴侶之间形成牢固的感情纽带，还可能是因为有助于人類建立長期伴侣關係，避免直接生育后代<ref name="Diamond"/><ref name="Reis">{{Cite book | author = Harry T. Reis | author2 = Susan Sprecher | author3 = Susan K. Sprecher | title = Encyclopedia of Human Relationships | volume = 1 | year = 2009 | publisher = SAGE | pages = 541–543 | isbn = 1412958466 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=3EkOwvSAtL4C&pg=PA541 | access-date = 2017-04-03 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170305195303/https://books.google.com/books?id=3EkOwvSAtL4C&pg=PA541 | archive-date = 2017-03-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。此一影響在人类中尤其明顯，其会加強社區中的協作行為。另外，性行為也增強了個體之間的社會性纽带，並有助更为龐大的社會結構的形成。由此産生的結果——協作，便成為了集體行動的誘因，並能以此增加群體之中每個個體生存的機會<ref name="Non-human"/> 。

===刺激方法及生理学===
在大多數哺乳動物當中，生殖器官的解剖特徵以及神經系統的某些迴路是特地為了異性間的交配而形成的，交配此一行為相當於一系列的本能性反應：[[勃起|勃起]]、陰道潤滑、[[脊柱前凸|脊柱前凸]]、臥下、插入、抽送、[[射精|射精]]。這些反應由[[激素|激素]]所制控，並受到性[[費洛蒙|費洛蒙]]的作用所軀使<ref name="Plant">{{Cite book|last1=Plant|first1=T.|last2=Zeleznik|first2= A.| year =2015| title =Knobil and Neill's Physiology of Reproduction| publisher = Academic Press|edition=4th}}</ref>。在[[人科|人科]]（包括人類）此一分類之下，一些控制交配的生物性因子已在演化過程中遭到修改<ref name="wunsch2017">{{cite journal |last1=Wunsch |first1=S |year=2017 |title=Phylogenesis of mammal sexuality. Analysis of the evolution of proximal factors |url=https://www.researchgate.net/publication/312407857_Phylogenesis_of_mammal_sexuality_Analysis_of_the_evolution_of_proximal_factors |journal=Sexologies |volume=26 |issue=1 |pages=e1-e10 |doi=10.1016/j.sexol.2016.12.001 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170221110245/https://www.researchgate.net/publication/312407857_Phylogenesis_of_mammal_sexuality_Analysis_of_the_evolution_of_proximal_factors |archivedate=2017-02-21 |access-date=2017-04-04 }}</ref>。就神經調控此一層面而言，那些變化在人類女性中尤其明顯。非靈長類動物的雌性只有在發情期期間才會進行交配<ref name="Pfaus2015"/>，但對於屬人科的雌性動物而言，她們在月經週期中的任何一點都可進行性交<ref name="Dixson2012">{{Cite book|last1=Dixson|first1=A.F|year=2012|url=https://global.oup.com/academic/product/primate-sexuality-9780199676613?cc=fr&lang=en&|title=Primate sexuality: Comparative studies of the Prosimians, Monkeys, Apes, and Human Beings|publisher=Oxford University Press|edition=2nd|access-date=2017-04-04|archive-date=2021-08-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210814122941/https://global.oup.com/academic/product/primate-sexuality-9780199676613?cc=fr&lang=en&|dead-url=no}}</ref>。儘管性費洛蒙會助長交配的反應<ref name="keller2009">{{cite journal|last1=Keller|first1=M|last2=Bakker|first2=J|year=2009|title=Special issue (12 articles) :  Pheromonal communication in higher vertebrates and its implication for reproductive function |journal =Behavioural Brain Research|pmc=2909619|pmid=19374009|volume =200|issue =2|pages=237-358}}</ref>，但人類檢測費洛蒙的能力已經遭到削弱<ref name="nei2008">{{cite journal|last1=Nei|first1= M.|last2=Niimura|first2=Y.|last3=Nozawa|first3=M.|year=2008|title=The evolution of animal chemosensory receptor gene repertoires: roles of chance and necessity|journal =Nat. Rev. Genet.|volume=9|issue =12|pages=951-963}}</ref><ref name="Zhang2003">{{cite journal|last1=Zhang|first1= J. |last2=Webb|first2=D.M.|year=2003|title= Evolutionary deterioration of the vomeronasal pheromone transduction pathway in catarrhine primates|journal =Proceedings of the National Academy of Sciences of the United States of America|volume =100|issue =14|pages=8337-8341}}</ref>，且只有很少的殘留影響<ref name="doty2014">{{cite book|last1=Doty|first1=R.L|year=2014|url=http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK200980/|chapter=Human Pheromones: Do They Exist?|editor=Mucignat-Caretta C|title=Neurobiology of Chemical Communication|publisher=CRC Press|isbn=978-1466553415|access-date=2017-04-04|archive-date=2021-09-30|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210930204249/http://www.ncbi.nlm.nih.gov/books/NBK200980/|dead-url=no}}</ref>。非靈長類動物的雌性会在交配过程中保持着脊柱前凸的狀態，但對於人類女性而言，此一反射基本毫无作用，且已被移除<ref name="Pfaus2015">{{cite book|last1=Pfaus|first1= J.G.| last2=Flanagan-Cato|first2= L.M.| last3= Blaustein|first3=J.D.|year=2015 |chapter=Female sexual behavior|veditors=Plant T,Zeleznik A,Knobil ,Neill||display-editors=2| title=Physiology of Reproduction|edition=4th|publisher = Academic Press}}</ref>。人類的性交跟其他哺乳動物的交配不同，其不是由激素所制控，或是受到性費洛蒙的作用所軀使，而是一種自願的習得性行为，目的是以此獲得生殖性的獎賞回饋<ref name="georgiadis2012">{{cite journal|last1= Georgiadis|first1= J.R.|last2=Kringelbach|first2= M.L.|last3= Pfaus |first3=J.G.|year=2012|title=Sex for fun: a synthesis of human and animal neurobiology|journal =Nat. Rev. Urol.|volume = 9|issue =9|pages=486-498}}</ref><ref name="wunsch2017"/>。

[[File:Édouard-Henri_Avril_(14).jpg|thumb]]對[[女上位|女上位]]的描繪——女上位是一种較为容易刺激陰蒂的体位<ref name="Roberts">{{cite book|title=Sex|publisher=Lotus Press|year=2006|page=145|isbn=8189093592|accessdate=2012-08-17|url=https://books.google.com/?id=zDS9kC03x2IC&pg=PA145&lpg=PA145|author=Keath Roberts}}</ref>]]
性交及其他性活動可包含各式各樣影响[[性刺激|性刺激]]的要素（[[刺激_(生理学)|生理刺激]]或[[心理刺激|心理刺激]]）在內，例如[[性交体位|性交体位]]的變化、[[性玩具|性玩具]]的使用情况<ref name="Weiten, 2008"/><ref name="Kar"/><ref name="Taormino">{{cite book|last=Taormino|first=Tristan|title=The Big Book of Sex Toys|publisher=Quiver|year=2009|accessdate=2014-06-09|page=52|isbn=978-1-59233-355-4|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Hfly-iMkWRkC&pg=PA52|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905081729/https://books.google.com/books?id=Hfly-iMkWRkC&pg=PA52|archive-date=2015-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在進行某些性活動之前，前戲亦可使伴侶得到充分的[[性喚起|性喚起]]，令[[陰莖|陰莖]]勃起，或使[[陰道|陰道]]得以潤滑<ref name="Weiten, 2011">{{cite book|title=Psychology Applied to Modern Life: Adjustment in the 21st Century|isbn =1-111-18663-4|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2011|pages=384–386|accessdate= 2012-01-05|url=https://books.google.com/?id=CGu96TeAZo0C&pg=PT421 |author1=Wayne Weiten |author2=Dana S. Dunn |author3=Elizabeth Yost Hammer }}</ref>。伴侣亦常常通過親吻、以帶有情欲的方式愛撫身體，來使另一方獲得性滿足，在性交过程中施行以上兩者亦能加强性滿足<ref name="Alters2">{{cite book | author = Sandra Alters | author2 = Wendy Schiff | title = Essential Concepts for Healthy Living Update | publisher = Jones & Bartlett Publishers | year = 2011 | page = 154 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | isbn = 144965374X | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=hTiFUEBStlkC&pg=PA154 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326124957/http://books.google.com/books?id=hTiFUEBStlkC&pg=PA154 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

在交配期間，伴侶可調整臀部的面向，以成一条直线，使得陰莖可在陰道內來回移動，引起摩擦，过程中陰莖通常沒有完全移離陰道。這種方式可使雙方都獲得刺激，並使單方或雙方都獲得高潮<ref name="Kahn, Fawcett"/><ref name="Starr2">{{cite book|title=Human Biology|isbn=0495561819|publisher=Cengage Learning|year=2008|page=314|accessdate=2013-04-30|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=09reWGhFDqUC&pg=PA314|author1=Cecie Starr|author2=Beverly McMillan|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131015091106/http://books.google.com/books?id=09reWGhFDqUC&pg=PA314|archive-date=2013-10-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

對於人類女性而言，刺激[[陰蒂|陰蒂]]常在性活動中起了一個關鍵的作用；70-80％的女性都須以對陰蒂進行刺激的方式來達至高潮<ref name="Flaherty">{{cite book|title=Psychiatry: Diagnosis & therapy. A Lange clinical manual|isbn = 0-8385-1267-4|publisher=[[McGraw-Hill|Appleton & Lange]] (Original from Northwestern University)|year=1993|pages=[https://archive.org/details/psychiatrydiagno00flah/page/544 544]|url=https://archive.org/details/psychiatrydiagno00flah|quote=The amount of time of sexual arousal needed to reach orgasm is variable — and usually much longer — in women than in men; thus, only 20–30% of women attain a coital climax. b. Many women (70–80%) require manual clitoral stimulation...|author1=Joseph A. Flaherty |author2=John Marcell Davis |author3=Philip G. Janicak }}</ref><ref name="Kenneth Mah">{{cite journal |vauthors=Mah K, Binik YM | title = The nature of human orgasm: a critical review of major trends | journal = Clinical Psychology Review | volume = 21 | issue = 6 | pages = 823–856 |date=2001-01-07 | pmid = 11497209 | doi = 10.1016/S0272-7358(00)00069-6 | quote = Women rated clitoral stimulation as at least somewhat more important than vaginal stimulation in achieving orgasm; only about 20% indicated that they did not require additional clitoral stimulation during intercourse.}}</ref><ref name="Kammerer-Doak">{{cite journal |vauthors=Kammerer-Doak D, Rogers RG | title = Female Sexual Function and Dysfunction | journal = Obstetrics and Gynecology Clinics of North America | volume = 35 | issue = 2 | pages = 169–183 |date=2008-06 | pmid = 18486835 | doi = 10.1016/j.ogc.2008.03.006 | quote = Most women report the inability to achieve orgasm with vaginal intercourse and require direct clitoral stimulation ... About 20% have coital climaxes...}}</ref>，但是間接刺激陰蒂亦可能足以令一些女士達至高潮，例如陰道交<ref name="Lloyd">{{cite book|author=Elisabeth Anne Lloyd|title=The case of the female orgasm: bias in the science of evolution|isbn=0-674-01706-4|publisher=Harvard University Press|year=2005|page=53|accessdate=2012-01-05|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=6GFNvA6TvlwC&pg=PA53|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130615012803/http://books.google.com/books?id=6GFNvA6TvlwC&pg=PA53|archive-date=2013-06-15|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="O'Connell">{{cite journal | vauthors = O'Connell HE, Sanjeevan KV, Hutson JM | title = Anatomy of the clitoris | journal = The Journal of Urology | volume = 174 | issue = 4 Pt 1 | pages = 1189–95 | date = 2005-10 | pmid = 16145367 | doi = 10.1097/01.ju.0000173639.38898.cd | laysummary = http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/5013866.stm | laydate = 2006-06-11 | laysource = [[BBC_News|BBC News]] | access-date = 2017-04-04 | archive-date = 2019-09-09 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20190909192820/http://news.bbc.co.uk/2/hi/health/5013866.stm | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一些伴侶可能因此選擇以[[女上位|女上位]]或{{link-en|貓式體位|coital alignment technique}}（一種結合[[傳教士式|傳教士式體位]]及施壓-反壓技術的性侵入體位）的方式去進行性交，以令刺激陰蒂的頻率最大化<ref name="Roberts"/><ref name="Kar"/><ref name="Hurlbert">{{cite journal |vauthors=Hurlbert DF, Apt C | title = The coital alignment technique and directed masturbation: a comparative study on female orgasm |url=https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-sex-and-marital-therapy_spring-1995_21_1/page/21 | journal = Journal of Sex & Marital Therapy | volume = 21 | issue = 1 | pages = 21–29 | year = 1995 | pmid = 7608994 | doi = 10.1080/00926239508405968 | laysummary =  | laydate =  | laysource =  }}</ref>。
