肛交的一般意思為將男性的陰莖插入其伴侣的直腸，以對[[肛門|肛門]]、肛門腔、括約肌瓣以及[[直腸|直腸]]等部位進行刺激的方式來獲取快感。但實踐者也可能把諸如性玩具和手指般的刺激源插入肛門，以此實現[[舔肛|舔肛]]和[[假陰莖肛交|假陰莖肛交]]<ref name="Answer">{{cite book|author=Barry R. Komisaruk|author2=Beverly Whipple|author3=Sara Nasserzadeh|author4=Carlos Beyer-Flores|title=The Orgasm Answer Guide|isbn=0-8018-9396-8|publisher=[[Johns_Hopkins_University_Press|JHU Press]]|year=2009|pages=108–109|accessdate=2011-11-06|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=Kkts3AX9QVAC&pg=PA108|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20130527225743/http://books.google.com/books?id=Kkts3AX9QVAC&pg=PA108|archive-date=2013-05-27|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

