=== 繁殖 ===
{{See|有性生殖|繁殖}}
[[File:Pregnancy_chance_by_day_near_ovulation.jpg|thumb]]
性交可能已有3.85億年的實踐歷史，地球上最古老的[[有颔下门|顎魚]]可能是第一種會通過交配繁衍後代的動物<ref>{{cite web |url=http://www.livescience.com/48400-origin-of-sex-found.html |title=Sex Is 385 Million Years Old, and It Looked Like Square Dancing |date=2014-10-22 |accessdate=2014-10-27 |website=Live Science |publisher= |last=Pappas |first=Stephanie |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170126120041/http://www.livescience.com/48400-origin-of-sex-found.html |archivedate=2017-01-26 }}</ref>。人類一般以陰莖－陰道交的方式繁殖下一代<ref name="Evan Jones">{{cite book|title=Human Reproductive Biology|isbn =0120884658|publisher=Academic Press|year=2006|pages=604<!-- As the title of the book implies, almost the entire book discusses this matter.-->|accessdate=2012-11-08|url=https://books.google.com/?id=pfiZfui2XLIC|author1=Richard Evan Jones |author2=Kristin H. López }}</ref>。男性性高潮一般會伴隨[[射精|射精]]，當中會發生一系列的[[肌肉收縮|肌肉收縮]]，把含有男性配子（[[精子|精子]]）的[[精液|精液]]從陰莖射至陰道內。精子後從阴道穹窿往[[子宮頸|子宮頸]]方向移動，進入子宮，再由子宮進入[[輸卵管|輸卵管]]。每次射精都有數以千萬甚至數以億計的精子射出，增加卵子受精的機會。當輸卵管中擁有能发育成新个体的卵子時，男性配子便會與卵子結合，導致[[受精|受精]]的出現，以及新的[[胚胎|胚胎]]形成。當胚胎到達子宮時，它会植入至子宮內膜——這意味着[[懷孕|懷孕]]的開始<ref name="Evan Jones"/><ref name="Starr3">{{cite book| author = Cecie Starr|author2= Beverly McMillan|title = Human Biology| publisher = Cengage Learning | year = 2015 | page = 339| accessdate = 2017-12-27 |isbn = 1305445945| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=lS5-BAAAQBAJ&pg=PT339}}</ref>。人類的性活動與大多數物種不同——其與發情期無關：在生殖週期的任何一點，以至懷孕途中，人類女性都可以進行性活動<ref name="Reis"/><ref>{{Cite book| author = Jared Diamond| author-link = Jared Diamond| title = Why Is Sex Fun? | year = 1997 | publisher = Basic Books | isbn = 0-465-03127-7}}</ref>。

因性交而懷孕的機會在排卵前約5天到排卵後1-2天為最高<ref>{{cite book|title=Taking Charge of Your Fertility|url=https://archive.org/details/takingchargeofyo00toni|last=Weschler|first=Toni|publisher=HarperCollins|year=2002|isbn=0-06-093764-5|edition=Revised|location=New York|pages=242、359–361}}</ref>。醫學上有建議指若要使懷孕機會最大化，人們便需每隔1-3天性交1次<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.mayoclinic.org/healthy-lifestyle/getting-pregnant/in-depth/how-to-get-pregnant/art-20047611|title=How to get pregnant|website=Mayo Clinic|date=2016-11-02|accessdate=2018-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170906155214/http://www.mayoclinic.org/healthy-lifestyle/getting-pregnant/in-depth/how-to-get-pregnant/art-20047611|archive-date=2017-09-06|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.nice.org.uk/guidance/cg156/ifp/chapter/trying-for-a-baby|title=Fertility problems: assessment and treatment, Clinical guideline [CG156]|website=National Institute for Health and Care Excellence|accessdate=2018-02-16|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180217082533/https://www.nice.org.uk/guidance/cg156/ifp/chapter/trying-for-a-baby|archive-date=2018-02-17|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。研究表明只要在過程中男方射精進入陰道，那麽不論他們採取哪一種性體位，懷孕機會也不会出现重大變化<ref name=americanpregnancy>{{cite web|url=http://americanpregnancy.org/getting-pregnant-ebook/p7M7O0q1c71703C/gettingpregnant.pdf|title=The Essential Guide to Getting Pregnant|website=American Pregnancy Association|author=Dr. Philip B. Imler & David Wilbanks|access-date=2018-05-06|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180601033115/http://americanpregnancy.org/getting-pregnant-ebook/p7M7O0q1c71703C/gettingpregnant.pdf|archive-date=2018-06-01|dead-url=yes}}</ref>。

一名[[捐精|捐精者]]只為放出精子，而跟並非他伴侣的女性進行性交的舉動一般稱為「自然[[授精|授精]]」，其跟[[人工授精|人工授精]]相反。人工授精是輔助生殖技術的形式之一，其透過完全或部分人工的手段去達至最终目的——懷孕<ref name="Bobick and Balaban">{{cite book|author1=James Bobick|author2=Naomi Balaban|title=The Handy Anatomy Answer Book|isbn=157859328X|publisher=Visible Ink Press|year=2008|pages=306–307|accessdate=2013-08-21|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=LBI2Sg2yYMoC&pg=PA305|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143718/http://books.google.com/books?id=LBI2Sg2yYMoC&pg=PA305|archive-date=2013-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。就人工授精的情況而言，捐精者会向精子庫捐獻精子，並以那些精子協助擁有明確懷孕意願的女性[[授精|授精]]。这一种醫學手段的目的某程度上等同性交<ref name="Sharma">{{cite book|author=R.K. Sharma|title=Concise Textbook Of Forensic Medicine & Toxicology|isbn=8131211452|publisher=[[Elsevier|Elsevier India]]|year=2007|pages=113–116|accessdate=2013-10-13|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=_zAwlKX_zNwC&pg=PA113|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143728/http://books.google.com/books?id=_zAwlKX_zNwC&pg=PA113|archive-date=2013-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="O'Toole">{{cite book|author=Mosby, Marie T. O'Toole|title=Mosby's Medical Dictionary|isbn=0323112587|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|year=2013|page=138|accessdate=2013-10-13|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=aW0zkZl0JgQC&pg=PA138|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143625/http://books.google.com/books?id=aW0zkZl0JgQC&pg=PA138|archive-date=2013-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。上述方法已被同性恋伴侣所應用。男同性伴侣可以以[[代孕|代孕]]的方式來獲得一名或數名子女，女同性伴侣則除了代孕之外，還可選擇异配授精<ref name="Berkowitz">{{cite journal |vauthors=Berkowitz D, Marsiglio W | year = 2007 | title = Gay Men: Negotiating Procreative, Father, and Family Identities | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_journal-of-marriage-and-family_2007-05_69_2/page/366| journal = Journal of Marriage and Family | volume = 69 | issue = 2| pages = 366–381 | doi = 10.1111/j.1741-3737.2007.00371.x }}</ref><ref name="Burda">{{Cite book| author = Joan M. Burda| title = Gay, lesbian, and transgender clients: a lawyer's guide | publisher = American Bar Association| year = 2008 |pages =69–74| isbn = 1-59031-944-3|accessdate=2011-07-28|url=https://books.google.com/?id=QdzB1f8Y8Q8C&pg=PA69}}</ref>。

===安全性行为和生育控制===
{{Main article|安全性行为|生育控制}}
{{See also|体外排精}}
不少异性和同性伴侣都有採用各種手段去達至[[安全性行为|安全性行为]]的目的，当中包括非插入式性行為<ref name="Kumar"/><ref name="Durham">{{cite book|title=The Person With HIV/AIDS: Nursing Perspectives|edition=3rd|isbn = 8122300049|publisher=Springer Publishing Company|year=2000|page=103|accessdate=2012-01-29|url=https://books.google.com/?id=WSCQ4L8kSXsC&pg=PA103|author1=Jerry D. Durham |author2=Felissa R. Lashley }}</ref>，异性伴侣也會把口交或/和肛交視为生育控制的方法<ref name="Crooks">{{cite book | title = Our Sexuality | publisher = Cengage Learning | year = 2010 | pages = 286–289 | accessdate =2012-08-30 |isbn = 0495812943| url = https://books.google.com/?id=MpRnPtmdRVwC&pg=PA286&lpg=PA286|quote=Noncoital forms of sexual intimacy, which have been called outercourse, can be a viable form of birth control. Outercourse includes all avenues of sexual intimacy other than penile–vaginal intercourse, including kissing, touching, mutual masturbation, and oral and anal sex. |author1=Robert Crooks |author2=Karla Baur }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Feldmann J, Middleman AB |title=Adolescent sexuality and sexual behavior |journal=Current opinion in obstetrics & gynecology |volume=14 |issue=5 |pages=489–493 |year=2002 |pmid=12401976 |url=http://journals.lww.com/co-obgyn/Abstract/2002/10000/Adolescent_sexuality_and_sexual_behavior.8.aspx |doi=10.1097/00001703-200210000-00008 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160430164746/http://journals.lww.com/co-obgyn/Abstract/2002/10000/Adolescent_sexuality_and_sexual_behavior.8.aspx |archivedate=2016-04-30 |access-date=2017-04-09 }}</ref>。若陰莖與陰道十分接近（比如[[股间性爱|股间性爱]]、互相摩擦生殖器），那么即使只進行肛交或其他性活動，女方仍有機會懷孕，當中精子會在阴道口附近沿着阴道的润滑液进入陰道。此外即使阴茎不靠近阴道，怀孕的风险仍然存在，因为沾有精液的手指或其他身体部分有可能会跟阴道接触，使得精子从此一途径進入阴道<ref>{{cite book|last=Thomas|first=R. Murray|title=Sex and the American teenager seeing through the myths and confronting the issues|year=2009|publisher=Rowman & Littlefield Education|location=Lanham, Md.|isbn=9781607090182|page=81|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=gM9EFgsJHyoC&pg=PA81|accessdate=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116155105/https://books.google.com/books?id=gM9EFgsJHyoC&pg=PA81|archive-date=2016-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Edlin|first=Gordon|title=Health & Wellness.|year=2012|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|isbn=9781449636470|page=213|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=csGk6j5rlN0C&pg=PA213|accessdate=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20161116175037/https://books.google.com/books?id=csGk6j5rlN0C&pg=PA213|archive-date=2016-11-16|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

安全性行为是一種跟{{link-en|緩減傷害|Harm reduction}}有關的理念<ref name="Who"/><ref name="Mercer">{{cite journal | vauthors = Chin HB, Sipe TA, Elder R, Mercer SL, Chattopadhyay SK, Jacob V, Wethington HR, Kirby D, Elliston DB, Griffith M, Chuke SO, Briss SC, Ericksen I, Galbraith JS, Herbst JH, Johnson RL, Kraft JM, Noar SM, Romero LM, Santelli J | title = The Effectiveness of Group-Based Comprehensive Risk-Reduction and Abstinence Education Interventions to Prevent or Reduce the Risk of Adolescent Pregnancy, Human Immunodeficiency Virus, and Sexually Transmitted Infections | journal = American Journal of Preventive Medicine | volume = 42 | issue = 3 | pages = 272–294 | year = 2012 | pmid = 22341164 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1016/j.amepre.2011.11.006 | url = http://www.ajpmonline.org/article/S0749-3797(11)00906-8/abstract | access-date = 2017-04-10 | archive-date = 2020-01-02 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20200102180246/https://www.ajpmonline.org/article/S0749-3797(11)00906-8/abstract | dead-url = no }}</ref> ，使用[[避孕套|避孕套]]則是安全性行为及生育控制的其中一種方式，其还被醫學界廣泛推舉为一种有效預防[[性傳染病|性傳染病]]的方法<ref name="Who"/><ref name="Mercer"/>。根据[[美國國立衛生研究院|美國國立衛生研究院]]及[[世界卫生组织|世界卫生组织]]的調查，相對於没有進行任何保护措施，正确及不間斷地使用乳胶安全套可使艾滋病的传播风险降低约85-99％<ref>{{cite conference |author=National Institute of Allergy and Infectious Diseases |author2=National Institutes of Health, Department of Health and Human Services |title=Workshop Summary: Scientific Evidence on Condom Effectiveness for Sexually Transmitted Disease (STD) Prevention |pages=13–15 |date=2001-07-20 |location=Hyatt Dulles Airport, Herndon, Virginia |url=http://www3.niaid.nih.gov/about/organization/dmid/PDF/condomReport.pdf |archiveurl=https://www.webcitation.org/5oFAVQUhH?url=http://www3.niaid.nih.gov/about/organization/dmid/PDF/condomReport.pdf |archivedate=2010-03-15 |format=PDF |accessdate=2009-03-20 |deadurl=yes }}</ref><ref name="WHO condoms">{{cite web|title=Effectiveness of male latex condoms in protecting against pregnancy and sexually transmitted infections|publisher=[[World_Health_Organization|World Health Organization]]|year=2000|accessdate=2013-07-23|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs243/en/index.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20100509064325/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs243/en/index.html|archivedate=2010-05-09|dead-url=no}}</ref>。避免感染性傳播疾病的最有效方法是避免發生性行為，特别是阴道/肛/口交<ref name="Mercer"/>。

與生育控制有關的决定和选择可能受当事人的文化背景所影響，比如宗教信仰、[[性别角色|性别角色]]，以及[[民俗|民俗]]<ref name="Hales2">{{cite book| title = An Invitation to Health: Choosing to Change| publisher = Cengage Learning| year = 2010| pages = 301–302| accessdate = 2013-03-30| isbn = 0538736550| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=yPa0LZXizO4C&pg=PA301| author = Dianne Hales| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131204033317/http://books.google.com/books?id=yPa0LZXizO4C&pg=PA301| archive-date = 2013-12-04| dead-url = no}}</ref>。在天主教为最大宗教的国家当中，比如爱尔兰、意大利和菲律宾，人們較为着重[[安全期|推算安全期避孕法]]及{{link-en|生育能力計劃生育法|Fertility awareness}}，並会反對使用其他避孕方法<ref name="Hales"/>。以全世界來計，[[絕育|絕育]]比以上兩种自然避孕法更为常见<ref name="Hales"/> 。於女性子宫置入[[子宮環|子宮環]]（IUD）則是最常见及最有效的可逆避孕方法<ref name="Hales"/><ref name=Winner2012>{{cite journal |vauthors=Winner B, Peipert JF, Zhao Q, Buckel C, Madden T, Allsworth JE, Secura GM | title = Effectiveness of long-acting reversible contraception | journal = N. Engl. J. Med. | volume = 366 | issue = 21 | pages = 1998–2007 | year = 2012 | pmid = 22621627 | doi = 10.1056/NEJMoa1110855 }}</ref>。在[[發展中國家|發展中國家]]，怀孕及避孕更为攸关生死，当中三份之一女性在20岁前就经歷至少一次分娩，但那些国家90％的{{link-en|不安全堕胎|Unsafe abortion}}都可以通过有效的避孕方式來预防<ref name="Hales"/>。

{{link-en|葛特馬赫研究所|Guttmacher Institute}}指出，在2002年，6200万名年齡介乎15-44岁的女性當中，就有62%至少采用一种避孕方法去避孕。在當時的美国，最普遍的避孕方法为服用[[避孕药|避孕药]]（30.6%），其次為输卵管结扎（27.0％）以及使用男用避孕套（18.0％），27%使用避孕用品的青少年女性則以避孕套为首選<ref name="Guttmacher 2">{{cite web|title=Contraceptive Use|publisher=Guttmacher Institute|year=2010|accessdate=2011-03-04|url=http://www.guttmacher.org/pubs/fb_contr_use.html|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131004232616/http://www.guttmacher.org/pubs/fb_contr_use.html|archive-date=2013-10-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。2014年，一份由{{link-en|凯泽家庭基金会|Kaiser Family Foundation}}發表的报告指出，在性活躍的美國青少年（年齡介乎15-19岁）當中，就有53％女性及66％男性报稱在上一次性交当中有使用避孕套；22.4％的青少年女性每日服用避孕藥去避孕<ref name="KFF_factsheet">{{cite web |url=http://www.kff.org/womenshealth/upload/3040-03.pdf |title=Sexual Health of Adolescents and Young Adults in the United States |accessdate=2017-05-19 |publisher=Kaiser Family Foundation |date=2014-08-20 |format=PDF |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111125123538/http://www.kff.org/womenshealth/upload/3040-03.pdf |archive-date=2011-11-25 |dead-url=yes }}</ref>。

在2010年，《{{link-en|美国性健康与行为调查|National Survey of Sexual Health and Behavior}}》（NSSHB）指出「美国国內有使用避孕套的阴道交達四分之一（若只計單身的則有三分之一）……黑人和西班牙裔美国人比白人和其他种族更常使用避孕套……在性唤醒、性愉悦和性高潮這些方面，有使用避孕套者跟没有使用者的程度大致相若<ref name="NSSHB">{{cite journal |title=Findings from the National Survey of Sexual Health and Behavior, Centre for Sexual Health Promotion, Indiana University |journal=The Journal of Sexual Medicine |volume=7, Supplement 5. |issue= |page=4 |year=2010 |pmid= |doi= |accessdate=2011-03-04 |url=https://kinseyinstitute.org/research/publications/faq.php |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170304153714/https://www.kinseyinstitute.org/research/publications/faq.php |archivedate=2017-03-04 |df= }}</ref>。」

===盛行率===
[[Image:Coition_of_a_Hemisected_Man_and_Woman.jpg|thumb]]於约1492年所绘的《男女性交解剖圖》（Coition of a Hemisected Man and Woman）表達了性交时身體內部会發生什麼。]]
「性交」一詞通常指的是陰莖－陰道交<ref name="Alters"/><ref name="Carroll"/>。研究表明，绝大多数异性伴侣几乎每次發生性行为时都会進行阴道交<ref name="Carroll"/>。美国性健康与行为调查在2010年指出陰道交是「最普遍的性行为，無分年龄、性别和种族<ref name="Carroll"/>。」克林特·布鲁斯（Clint E. Bruess）等人於2013年指出它是「一种最常被人研究的行为」，並表示在不同文化中，当人们提到「性行为」或「性交」时，往往是指「青少年性教育課程的重心<ref name="Bruess">{{cite book | author = Clint E. Bruess | author2 = Elizabeth Schroeder | title = Sexuality Education Theory and Practice | publisher = Jones & Bartlett Publishers | year = 2013 | page = 152 | accessdate = 2014-12-05 | isbn = 1449649289 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=WWFW6-kkAVoC&pg=PA152 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326113550/http://books.google.com/books?id=WWFW6-kkAVoC&pg=PA152 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。」韋騰（Weiten）等人指出性交是「在我們的社會中廣泛地受到認可和進行的性行為<ref name="Weiten3"/>。」

2009年，美國疾病控制與預防中心亦指出：「研究表明，不論年纪，口交都是一種經常在性活躍之男女和同性伴侣当中实践的性行為，包括青少年伴侣<ref name="CDC, oral sex"/>。」美国性健康与行为调查在2010年指出，陰道交遠比肛交（以插入方來計）常見，但仍有13-15％年齡介乎25-49岁的男性有从事过肛交（插入方）。在肛交中扮演接受方的男性則比扮演插入方的罕见，大约只有7％年齡介乎14-94岁的男性有在肛交中扮演接受方。它还宣稱从事肛交的女性較男性少，但仍不算罕見：估计10-14％年齡介乎18-39岁的女性在过去90天內有參與肛交，多數女性表示從事肛交的頻率为每月一次或一年數次<ref name="Carroll"/>。

此外研究者已對不同文化中性交的盛行率進行比較。2003年，{{link-en|法国國家人口統計研究院|Institut national d'études démographiques}}進行一項名為《什么时候男性和女性才会發生第一次性交?》（At what age do women and men have their first sexual intercourse?）的跨文化研究。其首先研究撒哈拉沙漠以南的非洲地區（馬里、塞內加爾和埃塞俄比亞）。數據表明，身处這些社會的男性的性啟蒙晚於女性，但通常發生於婚外。該研究認為[[印度次大陸|印度次大陸]]也包括在以上群体中，儘管相关數據只從[[尼泊尔|尼泊尔]]取得<ref name="Bozon">{{cite journal |last=Bozon |first=Michael |year=2003 |title=At what age do women and men have their first sexual intercourse? World comparisons and recent trends |journal=Population and Societies |volume=391 |pages=1–4 |issue= |url=https://www.ined.fr/fichier/s_rubrique/247/english_391.en.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304091955/https://www.ined.fr/fichier/s_rubrique/247/english_391.en.pdf |archivedate=2016-03-04 |access-date=2017-04-13 }}</ref><ref name="Caselli">{{cite book| author =  Graziella Caselli| author2 =  Guillaume Wunsch| author3 =  Daniel Courgeau| author4 =  Jacques Vallin| title =  Demography – Analysis and Synthesis: A Treatise in Population| publisher =  Academic Press| year =  2005| pages =  490–501| accessdate =  2013-09-06| isbn =  012765660X| url =  https://books.google.com/books?id=nmgNXoiAiU4C&pg=PA491| archive-url =  https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143552/http://books.google.com/books?id=nmgNXoiAiU4C&pg=PA491| archive-date =  2013-12-31| dead-url =  no}}</ref>。

數據表明，屬第二組的社会的家庭一般会鼓勵女兒晚婚，且在结婚前避免性活動。但卻会鼓勵兒子在婚前从老年女性或妓女身上獲得相关的經驗。身处這些社會的男性的性啟蒙早於女性。屬这组的社会包括[[南欧|南欧]]（葡萄牙、希臘和羅馬尼亞）和[[拉丁美洲|拉丁美洲]]（巴西、[[智利|智利]]和[[多明尼加|多明尼加]]）。該研究認為許多亞洲社會也屬於這一群體，儘管相关數據只從[[泰國|泰國]]獲得<ref name="Bozon"/><ref name="Caselli"/>。

在第三組，男性和女性的性啟蒙比較接近，但第三組之下又细分了兩个亚组。在非拉丁語系的天主教國家（比如波蘭和立陶宛）。性啟蒙开始得較遲，社会一般鼓勵晚婚，以及珍視男女的貞操。新加坡和斯里蘭卡的主流社会亦有类近的價值觀及行为模式。這項研究認為中國和越南也屬於這一組，儘管没从以上兩处地方獲得數據<ref name="Bozon"/><ref name="Caselli"/>。在北歐和東歐，性啟蒙的时間一般較早。且不論男女，一般都会从事婚前性交合，該研究把瑞士、德國和捷克歸类为此一組<ref name="Bozon"/><ref name="Caselli"/>。

1995年，美國的全国調查顯示，美國有至少3/4的男女在青少年晚期中進行过性交，超過2/3擁有性經驗的青少年有兩个或以上的性伴侶<ref name="Guttmacher 1">{{cite web|title=Sexual and Reproductive Health: Women and Men|publisher=Guttmacher Institute|year=2002|accessdate=2012-12-26|archivedate=2011-07-26|url=http://www.guttmacher.org/pubs/fb_10-02.html|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20110726135024/http://www.guttmacher.org/pubs/fb_10-02.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>。据[[美国卫生及公共服务部|美国卫生及公共服务部]]發表的《2002年家庭增长的全国调查》（2002 National Survey of Family Growth），15-44岁的受訪者平均首次性交年龄分別为17.3岁（女性）和17.0岁（男性）<ref name="New Age">{{cite web|url=http://www.newstrategist.com/productdetails/Sex.SamplePgs.pdf|title=Seventeen Is the Average Age at First Sexual Intercourse|accessdate=2013-03-23|publisher=newstrategist.com|work=American Sexual Behavior|format=PDF|archivedate=2013-01-16|archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20130116083609/http://www.newstrategist.com/productdetails/Sex.SamplePgs.pdf|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="CDC sr23_025">{{cite web |title=Fertility, Family Planning, and Reproductive Health of U.S.Women: Data From the 2002 National Survey of Family Growth |accessdate=2013-02-09 |publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC) |url=http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/series/sr_23/sr23_025.pdf |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160823054900/http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/series/sr_23/sr23_025.pdf |archivedate=2016-08-23 }}</ref><ref name="CDC sr23_026">{{cite web |title=Fertility, Contraception, and Fatherhood: Data on Men and Women From Cycle 6 (2002) of the National Survey of Family Growth |accessdate=2013-02-09 |publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC) |url=http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/series/sr_23/sr23_026.pdf |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507222700/http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/series/sr_23/sr23_026.pdf |archivedate=2017-05-07 }}</ref>。{{link-en|美国國家衛生統計中心|National Center for Health Statistics}}的特別表列顯示，2011年至2013年此一數字進一步下降至17.2岁（不論男女）<ref name="CDC abc_list_s">{{cite web |title=Key Statistics from the National Survey of Family Growth - S Listing |accessdate=2017-05-20 |publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC) |url=https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/nsfg/key_statistics/s.htm |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507210611/https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/nsfg/key_statistics/s.htm |archivedate=2017-05-07 }}</ref>。美國疾病控制與預防中心指出在2011-2013年，44.1％的女性和46.8％的男性在19岁或以前从事过至少一次性交<ref>{{cite web |title=Key Statistics from the National Survey of Family Growth - T Listing |url=https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/nsfg/key_statistics/t.htm |accessdate=2017-05-20 |publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC) |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507210624/https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/nsfg/key_statistics/t.htm |archivedate=2017-05-07 }}</ref>；43％美国未婚青少年女性及45.7％美国未婚青少年男性有从事过性交<ref>{{cite web |title=Key Statistics from the National Survey of Family Growth - P Listing |url=https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/nsfg/key_statistics/p.htm |accessdate=2017-05-20 |publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC) |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170507210539/https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/nsfg/key_statistics/p.htm |archivedate=2017-05-07 }}</ref>。中心还指出美国女性更多与比她們大1-3岁的男性发生首次性行为<ref name="CDC statistics">{{cite web |title=Teenagers in the United States: Sexual Activity, Contraceptive Use, and Childbearing, 2006–2010 National Survey of Family Growth |accessdate=2012-12-26 |publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC) |url=http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/series/sr_23/sr23_031.pdf |format=PDF |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170223051102/http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/series/sr_23/sr23_031.pdf |archivedate=2017-02-23 }}</ref>。

美国卫生及公共服务部在2002年的一份报告中指出，美国青少年首次从事性交及其他性活動的年齡正在延遲<ref name="CDC sr23_024">{{cite web|title=Teenagers in the United States: Sexual Activity, Contraceptive Use, and Childbearing, 2002|accessdate=2013-02-09|publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] (CDC)|url=http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/series/sr_23/sr23_024.pdf|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20121023210108/http://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/series/sr_23/sr23_024.pdf|archive-date=2012-10-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在1988-2002年間，15-19岁的美国未婚青少年男性从事性交的比率由60％下降至46％，女性則由51％下降至46％<ref name="CDC sr23_024" />。據一項在2013年發表於《[[柳葉刀_(雜誌)|柳葉刀]]》的英国全国調查顯示，英国兩性的平均首次性交年齡为17.0岁，16–24岁组則为16岁；60.7%的受訪者表示在过去4週中有从事过陰道性交；24.4%的受訪者表示在16岁以前有从事过性交；受訪者平均在其一生中擁有的性伴侣數量分別为4名（女性）及14.1名（男性）<ref>{{cite journal|authors=Mercer, Catherine H.|display-authors=etal|title=Changes in sexual attitudes and lifestyles in Britain through the life course and over time: findings from the National Surveys of Sexual Attitudes and Lifestyles (Natsal)|journal=The Lancet|volume=382|issue=9907 |pages=1781-94|year=2013|pmid=24286784|pmc=3899021|doi=10.1016/S0140-6736(13)62035-8}}</ref>。

據中國性學家[[潘绥铭|潘绥铭]]於2015年進行的調查顯示，60％的中國女性和40％的中國男性在20岁时已有过性交，25岁時則有90％左右<ref>{{cite web|title=“初夜”那点事|url=http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4dd47e5a0102wkx7.html|author=潘绥铭|date=2016-09-15|accessdate=2017-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170414043318/http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4dd47e5a0102wkx7.html|archive-date=2017-04-14|dead-url=yes}}</ref>，且未婚者中从來没有性生活者亦只有25％到33.3％（75％到66.7％有性生活），遠低於2000年時的數據（60-70％）<ref>{{cite web|title=婚前性行为（发布24）|author=潘绥铭|url=http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4dd47e5a0102w9b3.html|date=2016-04-20|accessdate=2017-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170414043405/http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4dd47e5a0102w9b3.html|archive-date=2017-04-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他亦在2010年的調查中指出，18到61岁的中國未婚者有过性交的比例已从2000年的37.7％升至2010年的49.1％；未婚男性与一个以上的人发生过性交的比例由15％升至45％左右，女性則由近乎0％升至30％<ref>{{cite web|title=谁在婚前守贞？|url=http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4dd47e5a0102v5m4.html|author=潘绥铭|date=2014-10-29|accessdate=2017-04-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170415011940/http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4dd47e5a0102v5m4.html|archive-date=2017-04-15|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

據[[香港家庭計劃指導會|香港家庭計劃指導會]]於2016年為年齡介乎18-27歲的青年進行的調查顯示，44.5%的男性及43.6%的女性從事過性交，已從事過性交的男性及女性平均首次性交的年齡分別為18.5歲及19.0歲，為歷年調查中最高<ref name=“HKFP2016”>{{cite book|title=the report of young sexually 2016|chapter =Aged 18-27 Youths|author =the family planning association of Hong Kong|year=2017|isbn=978-962-7435-53-2}}</ref>{{rp|63-64}}。89.7%及90.7%過去6个月有從事性交的男女進行過避孕<ref name=“HKFP2016”/>{{rp|68}}。以它為首選的男女分別有92.0%及86.0%<ref name=“HKFP2016”/>{{rp|71}}。約6.6%及13.8%的受訪男女曾使人懷孕/經歷懷孕最少1次<ref name=“HKFP2016”/>{{rp|90}}。

==與健康的關係==
===好處===
性行為和性活動通常能为人類帶來好處。比如其會增加體内的[[抗體|抗體]]產生、降低[[血壓|血壓]]，从而使免疫力得以增強<ref name="Steptoe">{{cite book| author = Andrew Steptoe| author2 = Kenneth Freedland| author3 = J. Richard Jennings| author4 = Maria M. Llabre| author5 = Stephen B Manuck| author6 = Elizabeth J. Susman| title = Handbook of Behavioral Medicine: Methods and Applications| publisher = Springer Science & Business Media| year = 2010| pages = 60–61| accessdate = 2014-12-07| isbn = 0387094881| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=Si9TtI5AGIEC&pg=PA60| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326112244/http://books.google.com/books?id=Si9TtI5AGIEC&pg=PA60| archive-date = 2015-03-26| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Hornstein">{{cite book | author = Theresa Hornstein | author2 = Jeri Schwerin | title = Biology of Women | publisher = Cengage Learning | year = 2012 | page = 205 | accessdate = 2014-12-07 | isbn = 1285401026 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=ibgKAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA205 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326131542/http://books.google.com/books?id=ibgKAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA205 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，並会降低男性患上[[前列腺癌|前列腺癌]]的風險<ref name="Steptoe"/>。性親密和性高潮還會使體内[[催产素|催产素]]的水平增加，其有助加強人與人之間的感情紐帶和信任<ref name="Hornstein"/><ref name="Sigelman">{{cite book | author = Carol Sigelman | author2 = Elizabeth Rider | title = Life-Span Human Development | publisher = Cengage Learning | year = 2011 | page = 452 | accessdate = 2014-12-07 | isbn = 1111342733 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=8smBuRecmDsC&pg=PT480 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326114446/http://books.google.com/books?id=8smBuRecmDsC&pg=PT480 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。據信，催產素對女性的影響比男性大，这可能是女性更常把性吸引力/性行為跟戀愛和愛情聯繫起來的原因<ref name="Freberg"/>。臨床神經心理學家大衛·威克斯（David Weeks）進行了一項持續10年的長期研究，当中包括3500位年齡介乎18歲至102歲的測試對象。並在研究開始後的第10年客观地为受試者的照片評分。结果發現定期的性行為有助使人看起來更为年轻<ref>{{cite book|last=Northrup|first=Christiane|title=Women's Bodies, Women's Wisdom: Creating Physical and Emotional Health and Healing|year=2010|publisher=Bantam|isbn=978-0-553-80793-6|page=232|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=V9S3keMnie8C&pg=PA232&lpg=PA232|accessdate=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905090634/https://books.google.com/books?id=V9S3keMnie8C&pg=PA232&lpg=PA232|archive-date=2015-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

===風險===
[[细菌|细菌]]、[[病毒|病毒]]、[[寄生|寄生物]]可经由性接觸傳染（尤其是插入式性行為），造成[[性傳染病|性傳染病]]。諸如[[愛滋病|愛滋病]]和[[梅毒|梅毒]]般的「性傳染病」亦可经由其他方式傳播，比如[[分娩|母嬰傳播]]、血液傳播、共用針筒<ref name="WHO 2015">{{cite web |title=性传播感染 |publisher=世卫组织 |url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs110/zh/ |date=2016-08 |accessdate=2017-05-18 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170420114714/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs110/zh/ |archivedate=2017-04-20 }}</ref>。受到[[淋球菌|淋球菌]]或[[衣原體感染|衣原體感染]]的女性早期通常不會有任何症狀出現，或不知道自己已被感染<ref name="性学觀止">{{cite book|date=2009-12|title=性學觀止|author=賀兰特·凱查杜里安|publisher=世界圖書出版公司|isbn=978-7-5062-8688-6}}</ref>{{rp|126-127}}。未經妥善治療的衣原體感染可導致女性不育和[[異位妊娠|異位妊娠]]，梅毒則可導致[[死產|死產]]和新生兒死亡。未經妥善治療的淋病可引致[[流产|流产]]、[[早產|早產]]，以及[[新生兒死亡|新生兒死亡]]。若某孩子的母亲在妊娠的同时患有未经妥善治療的淋病或衣原體感染，則可能会導致該名孩子患上{{link-en|新生兒結膜炎|Neonatal conjunctivitis}}（嚴重的眼睛感染），嚴重者或会失明<ref name="WHO 2015"/>。[[乙型肝炎|乙型肝炎]]也可通过性接觸傳染<ref>{{cite web |title=CDC Hepatitis B Information for Health Professionals |url=http://www.cdc.gov/hepatitis/HBV/HBVfaq.htm#treatment |date=2016-08-04 |accessdate=2017-05-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170515131212/http://www.cdc.gov/hepatitis/HBV/HBVfaq.htm#treatment |archivedate=2017-05-15 }}</ref> 。全球約有2.57亿人是慢性乙肝攜帶者<ref>{{cite web |title=乙型肝炎 |work=实况报道 |date=2017-04 |url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs204/zh/ |publisher=世卫组织 |accessdate=2017-05-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161031001456/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs204/zh/ |archivedate=2016-10-31 }}</ref>。

美國每年有近2000萬例新的性傳染病个案<ref>{{cite web |title=CDC Fact Sheet: Reported STDs in the United States |url=https://www.cdc.gov/nchhstp/newsroom/docs/factsheets/std-trends-508.pdf |publisher=[[Centers_for_Disease_Control_and_Prevention|Centers for Disease Control and Prevention]] |year=2016 |accessdate=2017-05-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170430043906/https://www.cdc.gov/nchhstp/newsroom/docs/factsheets/std-trends-508.pdf |archivedate=2017-04-30 }}</ref>。在2016年，世界衛生組織估計每年约有3.57亿人感染可治癒的性傳播疾病（比如梅毒、淋病和衣原體感染），每天有100多万例新的性傳染病个案<ref name="WHO 2015"/>。某些性傳染病可引起{{link-en|生殖器潰瘍|Genital ulcer}}；即使沒有潰瘍，也使得人類免疫缺陷病毒感染和傳染的风險各增加了10倍<ref name="WHO 2015"/>。人類免疫缺陷病毒是世界头号的傳染性殺手之一：在2015年有估計指出，自人类免疫缺陷病毒疫情開始以來，已有約3500萬人因其死亡。2015年的估計亦指出全球约70％人类免疫缺陷病毒感染者來自非洲。「撒哈拉以南非洲地區仍然受到最嚴重的影響，每25名成年人就有1名（4.4％）是人类免疫缺陷病毒感染者<ref name=WHO-HIV>{{cite web|title=HIV/AIDS|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs360/zh/|publisher=[[World_Health_Organization|World Health Organization]]|accessdate=2017-05-18|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517145502/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs360/zh/|archive-date=2017-05-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。」其可通過血液检测來診斷。儘管目前无法治愈人类免疫缺陷病毒感染，但可以通過[[抗反轉錄病毒藥物|抗逆转录病毒治疗]]來控制病情，人类免疫缺陷病毒携带者仍可以享有健康且有益的生活<ref name=WHO-2012>{{cite web|title=艾滋病毒/艾滋病|url=http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs360/zh/|work=实况报道|publisher=世卫组织|accessdate=2017-05-18|date=2016-11|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170517145502/http://www.who.int/mediacentre/factsheets/fs360/zh/|archive-date=2017-05-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

早期醫療介入對所有懷疑人類免疫缺陷病毒感染者都是有好处的，美國疾病控制與預防中心表示：「跟人類免疫缺陷病毒携带者從事口交的風險遠低於肛交或阴道性交……但是要準確衡量因为口交而傳播病毒的風險仍是十分困難……因为許多性活躍的人在一次性经驗中除了会進行口交之外，还会進行其他形式的性活動，比如肛交或/和阴交，所以人類免疫缺陷病毒一旦傳染，便很難確定是那种性活動所導致……幾個相關因子会增加口交时傳播病毒的風險，包括潰瘍、牙齦出血、生殖器皰疹，和患上其他性傳染病<ref name="CDC, oral sex"/>。」

2012年全球约有2.13亿例怀孕个案，当中大約有8490万例（40％）屬意外怀孕，主要地区中約有50％的意外怀孕个案選擇[[墮胎|墮胎]]，38％的个案順利分娩，其餘的則流产<ref>{{cite journal|last1=Sedgh|first1=G.|last2=Singh|first2=S.|last3=Hussain|first3=R.|year=2014|title= Intended and unintended pregnancies worldwide in 2012 and recent trends|journal =Studies in family planning|volume = 45 | issue = 3|pages=301-14|doi=10.1111/j.1728-4465.2014.00393.x|PMC=4727534}}</ref><ref>{{cite web|title=New Study Finds That 40% of Pregnancies Worldwide Are Unintended|url=https://www.guttmacher.org/news-release/2014/new-study-finds-40-pregnancies-worldwide-are-unintended|date=2014-09-17|accessdate=2017-05-22|publisher=Guttmacher Institute|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170520191818/https://www.guttmacher.org/news-release/2014/new-study-finds-40-pregnancies-worldwide-are-unintended|archive-date=2017-05-20|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在1990年至2008年間，美國[[青少年懷孕|青少年懷孕]]率下降了40％，从1000名青少年女性（15-19岁）中有116.3名懷孕下降至69.8名。以上數據包括活產、墮胎和流產<ref name="Ventura">{{cite journal|last1=Ventura|first1=S. J.|last2=Curtin|first2=S. C.|last3=Abma|first3=J. C|last4=Henshaw|first4=S. K|year=2012|title=Estimated pregnancy rates and rates of pregnancy outcomes for the United States, 1990-2008. National vital statistics reports: from the Centers for Disease Control and Prevention, National Center for Health Statistics|url=https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/nvsr/nvsr60/nvsr60_07.pdf|journal=National Vital Statistics System|volume=60|issue=7|pages=1-21|author=|access-date=2017-05-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170404225011/https://www.cdc.gov/nchs/data/nvsr/nvsr60/nvsr60_07.pdf|archive-date=2017-04-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>。在2008年，共有约1750萬例青少年分娩以及墮胎个案發生於發達国家<ref>{{cite web|title=Adolescent Pregnancy and Its Outcomes Across Countries|url=https://www.guttmacher.org/fact-sheet/adolescent-pregnancy-and-its-outcomes-across-countries|accessdate=2017-05-22|date=2015-08|publisher=Guttmacher Institute|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170303075627/https://www.guttmacher.org/fact-sheet/adolescent-pregnancy-and-its-outcomes-across-countries|archive-date=2017-03-03|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

性活動能增加基因[[轉錄因子|轉錄因子]][[ΔFosB|ΔFosB]] 於[[伏隔核|大腦獎勵中心]]的表達<ref name="ΔFosB reward">{{cite journal |vauthors=Blum K, Werner T, Carnes S, Carnes P, Bowirrat A, Giordano J, Oscar-Berman M, Gold M | title = Sex, drugs, and rock 'n' roll: hypothesizing common mesolimbic activation as a function of reward gene polymorphisms | journal = J. Psychoactive Drugs | volume = 44 | issue = 1 | pages = 38–55 | year = 2012 | pmid = 22641964 | pmc = 4040958 | doi = 10.1080/02791072.2012.662112}}</ref><ref name="Natural and drug addictions">{{cite journal | author = Olsen CM | title = Natural rewards, neuroplasticity, and non-drug addictions | journal = Neuropharmacology | volume = 61 | issue = 7 | pages = 1109–1122 |date=2011-12  | pmid = 21459101 | pmc = 3139704 | doi = 10.1016/j.neuropharm.2011.03.010 | url = }}</ref><ref name="Amph and sex addiction"><!--Supplemental primary source-->{{cite journal |vauthors=Pitchers KK, Vialou V, Nestler EJ, Laviolette SR, Lehman MN, Coolen LM | title = Natural and drug rewards act on common neural plasticity mechanisms with ΔFosB as a key mediator | journal = J. Neurosci. | volume = 33 | issue = 8 | pages = 3434–42 |date=2013-02  | pmid = 23426671 | pmc = 3865508 | doi = 10.1523/JNEUROSCI.4881-12.2013 }}</ref>。因此，經常（每日）參與性活動可能会導致ΔFosB的過度表達，誘發当事人對性活動沉溺（性沉溺是指強迫性地參與性活動，儘管可能会为自己带來負面後果<ref name="NHM addiction-reward-reinforcement">{{cite book |vauthors=Malenka RC, Nestler EJ, Hyman SE |veditors=Sydor A, Brown RY | title = Molecular Neuropharmacology: A Foundation for Clinical Neuroscience |url=https://archive.org/details/molecularneuroph00nest | year = 2009 | publisher = McGraw-Hill Medical | location = New York | isbn = 9780071481274 | pages = [https://archive.org/details/molecularneuroph00nest/page/364 364]–365, 375 | edition = 2nd | chapter = Chapter 15: Reinforcement and Addictive Disorders | quote= The defining feature of addiction is compulsive, out-of-control drug use, despite negative consequences. ...<br />compulsive eating, shopping, gambling, and sex–so-called "natural addictions"– ... Indeed, addiction to both drugs and behavioral rewards may arise from similar dysregulation of the mesolimbic dopamine system.}}</ref>，比如影響个人生活、工作以及社交<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.webmd.com/sexual-conditions/features/is-sex-addiction-real#1|title=Is Sex Addiction Real?|last=McMillen|first=Matt|date=2013-03-27|accessdate=2017-04-16|publisher=WebMD|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170417073001/http://www.webmd.com/sexual-conditions/features/is-sex-addiction-real#1|archive-date=2017-04-17|dead-url=no}}</ref>，不過至今仍沒有任何臨床診斷標準納入性癮這一狀態，現在尚未生效的ICD-11<nowiki>只納入了</nowiki>[[強迫性性行為|強迫性性行為]]，且需在不考慮道德及社會不贊成這些因素的情況下，符合「儘管有不良後果或者只有很少/根本沒有得到滿足，仍會繼續重複進行性行為」這一條條件<ref>[https://www.usatoday.com/news/health/2010-02-10-dsm10_ST_N.htm Psychiatry's bible: Autism, binge-eating updates proposed for 'DSM'] {{Wayback|url=https://www.usatoday.com/news/health/2010-02-10-dsm10_ST_N.htm |date=20110628215628 }} USA Today.</ref><ref>{{Cite news|url=https://edition.cnn.com/2018/07/10/health/compulsive-sexual-behavior-mental-health-condition/index.html|title=WHO classifies compulsive sexual behavior as mental health condition|last=CNN|first=Jen Christensen,|work=CNN|access-date=2018-11-26|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190205175019/https://edition.cnn.com/2018/07/10/health/compulsive-sexual-behavior-mental-health-condition/index.html|archive-date=2019-02-05|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref>{{Cite web|url=https://icd.who.int/browse11/l-m/en#/http://id.who.int/icd/entity/1630268048|title=ICD-11 - Mortality and Morbidity Statistics|website=icd.who.int|language=en|access-date=2018-11-26|archive-url=https://archive.today/20180801205234/https://icd.who.int/browse11/l-m/en%23/http://id.who.int/icd/entity/294762853#/http://id.who.int/icd/entity/1630268048|archive-date=2018-08-01|dead-url=no}}</ref> ）<ref name="ΔFosB reward" /><ref name="Natural and drug addictions" /><ref name="Amph and sex addiction" />。[[性沉溺|性沉溺]]或[[性慾亢進|性慾亢進]]通常遭認為是一种衝動控制疾患，或是行為沉溺的一种。它已被認为跟多巴胺这种神經遞質的水平異常有关。其特點在於过份执迷於性交，以及失去相关的控制能力。有建議認为DSM-5應把這種「沉溺行為」归类为强迫型人格障碍。它亦遭認為跟遺傳因子有關。沉溺性交者的大腦對視覺性的性暗示有着較活躍的反應。尋求治療的患者通常會会見一名醫師，以便進行藥物治疗，以及其他疗法<ref name="Probstvan Eimeren2013">{{cite journal|last1=Probst|first1=Catharina C.|last2=van Eimeren|first2=Thilo|title=The Functional Anatomy of Impulse Control Disorders|journal=Current Neurology and Neuroscience Reports|volume=13|issue=10|year=2013|issn=1528-4042|doi=10.1007/s11910-013-0386-8|pmid=23963609|pmc=3779310}}</ref>。[[克萊恩-萊文症候群|克萊恩-萊文症候群]]是其中一种会導致患者性慾亢進的疾病，它的臨床表現包括嗜睡及性慾亢進，但是此一疾病的患者十分罕見<ref name="GuilleminaultMiglis2014">{{cite journal|last1=Guilleminault|first1=Christian|last2=Miglis|first2=Mitchell|title=Kleine-Levin syndrome: a review|url=https://archive.org/details/pubmed-PMC3901778|journal=Nature and Science of Sleep|year=2014|page=19|issn=1179-1608|doi=10.2147/NSS.S44750}}</ref>。

[[性猝死|性活動可能会導致猝死]]，尤其是透過冠狀動脈疾病所引起的，此一死法有时会被稱为性猝死、性交猝死，或馬上风<ref name="Kahn, Fawcett"/><ref name="Kipshidze">{{Cite book|author= Nicolas Kipshidze|author2= Jawad Fareed|author3= Patrick W. Serruys|author4= Jeff Moses|title= Textbook of Interventional Cardiovascular Pharmacology|year= 2007|publisher= CRC Press|page= 505|isbn= 0203463048|url= https://books.google.com/books?id=13g_niZy0usC&pg=PA505|accessdate= 2015-10-21|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150905083344/https://books.google.com/books?id=13g_niZy0usC&pg=PA505|archive-date= 2015-09-05|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="Dahabreh">{{cite journal|last=Dahabreh|first=Issa J.|title=Association of Episodic Physical and Sexual Activity With Triggering of Acute Cardiac Events. Systematic Review and Meta-analysis.|journal=JAMA: The Journal of the American Medical Association|date=2011-03-23|volume=305|issue=12|page=1225|doi=10.1001/jama.2011.336|quote=Acute cardiac events were significantly associated with episodic physical and sexual activity; this association was attenuated among persons with high levels of habitual physical activity.}}</ref> ，但性猝死的情況十分罕見<ref name="Kipshidze"/>。日常運動量少的人一旦進行性交或高強度運動时，其[[心肌梗死|心臟病發作]]或[[心搏停止|猝死]]的風險便会略有增加<ref name="Dahabreh"/>。虽然定期鍛煉可以減少相关風險，但仍不能完全消去<ref name="Dahabreh"/>。瑞士的一項研究指出，所有跟性交有關的急症室求診个案中，只有少於1％为[[心肌梗死|心血管疾病]]，10％的个案为[[創傷|創傷]]，神经系统疾病的則有12％，当中最常見的是頭痛，佔了49％。其后則是{{link-en|短暫性全面腦失憶|Transient global amnesia}}（20％）以及[[蛛网膜下腔出血|蛛网膜下腔出血]]（22％）<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Pfortmueller CA, Koetter JN, Zimmermann H, Exadaktylos AK | title = Sexual activity-related emergency department admissions: Eleven years of experience at a Swiss university hospital | journal = Emergency Medicine Journal | volume = 30 | issue = 10 | pages = 846–850 | year = 2012 | pmid = 23100321 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1136/emermed-2012-201845 }}</ref>。

===持續時間及相關障礙===
{{see also|陰道內射精延遲時間|保留性交}}
若某次性交牽涉到一名男性的參與，那麼男方一旦射精，該次性交往往便就此結束，但其伴侣有可能尚未達至[[性高潮|高潮]]<ref name="Wincze">{{Cite book| author = John Wincze| title = Enhancing Sexuality : A Problem-Solving Approach to Treating Dysfunction| year = 2009| publisher = [[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]]| pages = 56–60| isbn = 0199718024| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=8YxbeHsgiGMC&pg=PA56| access-date = 2017-04-17| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170305115104/https://books.google.com/books?id=8YxbeHsgiGMC&pg=PA56| archive-date = 2017-03-05| dead-url = no}}</ref>。[[早發性射精|早發性射精]]對男士而言亦是十分普遍的現象，女性往往需花比男方更長的時間才能在性伴侣的刺激底下達至高潮<ref name="Weiten, 2011"/><ref name="Porst">{{cite book|author = Hartmut Porst|author2 = Jacques Buvat|title = Standard Practice in Sexual Medicine|publisher = John Wiley & Sons|year = 2008|accessdate = 2013-10-22|page = 189|isbn = 1405178728|url = https://books.google.com/books?id=S4GJio79XOUC&pg=PA189|archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326131235/http://books.google.com/books?id=S4GJio79XOUC&pg=PA189|archive-date = 2015-03-26|dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Emmanuele">{{cite book |author = Emmanuele A. Jannini |author2 = Chris G. McMahon |author3 = Marcel D. Waldinger |title = Premature Ejaculation: From Etiology to Diagnosis and Treatment |publisher = Springer |year = 2012 |accessdate = 2013-10-22 |pages = 159–162 |isbn = 8847026466 |url = https://books.google.com/books?id=iCXF3sWtgegC&pg=PA159 |archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326112201/http://books.google.com/books?id=iCXF3sWtgegC&pg=PA159 |archive-date = 2015-03-26 |dead-url = no }}</ref>。[[麥斯特與強生|麥斯特與強生]]在他們的研究中發現，男性在與伴侶進行性交時，每位平均花約4分鐘便達至高潮，但在同樣情況之下，女性卻要花10-20分鐘才能達至高潮。相比下，女性以自慰達至高潮的時間就短很多：每位平均約花4分鐘<ref name="Weiten, 2011"/>。諸如魏滕（Weiten）般的学者指出：「許多伴侶都拘泥於『只應以性交（陰道交）來達至高潮』此一無謂的想法上……以至『前戲』此一用詞都在暗示它只是一項『事前準備』……因為女性在陰道交之中較難高潮的關係，所以她們更有可能會[[假裝高潮|假裝高潮]]<ref name="Weiten, 2011"/>。」
