金賽研究所的学者們在1991年指出：「从插入陰道到射精之間的時間不僅因人而異，在同一男士中亦会有所變化……雙方皆滿意的性交持续时间便是最合适的時長」，他們还强调道：「虽然金賽發現75％的男性在插入后2分鐘內便会射精，但他並没有詢問這些男性或他們的伴侶是否對2分鐘的持续时间感到滿意……最近許多的研究報告都指出性交的持续时间稍比金賽所發現的長<ref name="Reinisch">{{cite book | title = The Kinsey Institute New Report On Sex| publisher =Macmillan | year = 1991 | pages = 129–130| accessdate =2012-08-30 |isbn = 0312063865| url = https://books.google.com/?id=KsW6wPiXEd0C&pg=PA129&lpg=PA129 |author1=June M. Reinisch |author2=Ruth Beasley }}</ref>。」2008年，一份訪問加拿大和美國的[[性治疗|性治療師]]的調查指出，異性交媾（性交）的平均持續时間为7分鐘，1-2分鐘則过短，3-7分鐘为适当，最理想的持续时间为7-13分鐘，但持续10-30分鐘的性交則反而过長<ref name="Carroll"/><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Corty EW, Guardiani JM | title = Canadian and American Sex Therapists' Perceptions of Normal and Abnormal Ejaculatory Latencies: How Long Should Intercourse Last? | journal = The Journal of Sexual Medicine | volume = 5 | issue = 5 | pages = 1251–1256 | year = 2008 | pmid = 18331255 | pmc =  | doi = 10.1111/j.1743-6109.2008.00797.x }}</ref>。

在充足的刺激底下難以達至高潮的情況一般稱為[[高潮障礙|高潮障礙]]，其会使当事人感到沮喪<ref name="Bullough">{{cite book|author=Vern L Bullough, RN, PhD|author2=Bonnie Bullough|title=Human Sexuality: An Encyclopedia|publisher=[[Routledge|Routledge]]|page=32|year=2014|accessdate=2014-12-06|isbn=1135825025|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=-cqlAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA32|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326113552/http://books.google.com/books?id=-cqlAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA32|archive-date=2015-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。高潮障礙常見發生於女性身上，且較男性患者多<ref name="Rosenthal">{{cite book|first= Martha|last= Rosenthal|title= Human Sexuality: From Cells to Society|publisher= Cengage Learning|year= 2012|page= 150|accessdate= 2013-10-22|isbn= 9780618755714|url= https://books.google.com/books?id=d58z5hgQ2gsC&pg=PT170|archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150326125259/http://books.google.com/books?id=d58z5hgQ2gsC&pg=PT170|archive-date= 2015-03-26|dead-url= no}}</ref><ref name="Weiner2">{{cite book |author =Irving B. Weiner |author2 =George Stricker |author3 =Thomas A. Widiger |title =Handbook of Psychology, Clinical Psychology |publisher =John Wiley & Sons |year =2012 |accessdate =2013-10-22 |pages =172–175 |isbn =1118404432 |url =https://books.google.com/books?id=A_NaK3cwQSsC&pg=PA172 |archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326113719/http://books.google.com/books?id=A_NaK3cwQSsC&pg=PA172 |archive-date =2015-03-26 |dead-url =no }}</ref>，這可歸因於缺乏關注女性身體的[[性教育|性教育]]，使人們缺乏諸如「刺激陰蒂通常是女性性高潮的關鍵」般的知識，此一現象在[[反性主义|反性文化]]中特別常見<ref name="Weiner2"/>。用於性交的身体结构較不利於刺激陰蒂，但有利于刺激陰莖；伴侣通常需以手指、口舌等刺激源對陰蒂的外部進行刺激，才能使女方達至高潮<ref name="Weiten, 2011"/>。大約25％的女性自感難以達至高潮<ref name="Carroll"/>，10％則從來沒體驗過一次高潮<ref name="Plotnik">{{cite book |author1=Rod Plotnik |author2=Haig Kouyoumdjian |title =Introduction to Psychology| publisher = Cengage Learning | year = 2010 | page = 344|isbn = 0495903442| quote= Inhibited female orgasm refers to a persistent delay or absence of orgasm after becoming aroused and excited. About 10% of women never reach orgasm...}}</ref>。4-5成的女性則對性生活存有不滿或在一生的某個階段體會過性喚起困難<ref name="Knoepp">{{cite journal |vauthors=Knoepp LR, Shippey SH, Chen CC, Cundiff GW, Derogatis LR, Handa VL | title = Sexual complaints, pelvic floor symptoms, and sexual distress in women over forty | journal = The Journal of Sexual Medicine | volume = 7 | issue = 11 | pages = 3675–82 | year = 2010 | pmid = 20704643 | pmc = 3163299 | doi = 10.1111/j.1743-6109.2010.01955.x }}</ref>。

[[陰道痙攣|陰道痙攣]]是指因为骨盆底肌肉无意识地绷紧，而令女方在性交或往陰道插入任何物件时感到痛苦，甚至不可能進行任何形式的插入。它是由恥骨尾骨肌（或稱PC肌）的條件反射所引起的。陰道痙攣對某些女性而言是難以克服的，因為如果一名女性預期在性交過程中會感到疼痛，便有机会引致陰道痙攣，繼而使自我預言成真<ref name="Weiner2"/><ref name="Ferri">{{cite book|author=Fred F. Ferri|title=Ferri's Clinical Advisor 2013,5 Books in 1, Expert Consult — Online and Print,1: Ferri's Clinical Advisor 2013|publisher=Elsevier Health Sciences|isbn=0323083730|year=2012|page=1134|accessdate=2014-11-29|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=OR3VERnvzzEC&pg=PA1134|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326122056/http://books.google.com/books?id=OR3VERnvzzEC&pg=PA1134|archive-date=2015-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。治療陰道痙攣一般需從心理及行為這兩方面入手，比如陰道擴張器練習<ref name="Goldman">{{cite book |author= Marlene B. Goldman |author2= Rebecca Troisi |author3= Kathryn M. Rexrode |title= Women and Health |publisher= Academic Press |page= 351 |year= 2012 |accessdate= 2014-12-06 |isbn= 0123849799 |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=mavb4v8w8bsC&pg=PA351 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150326120926/http://books.google.com/books?id=mavb4v8w8bsC&pg=PA351 |archive-date= 2015-03-26 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。此外已有測試證实[[肉毒桿菌毒素|肉毒桿菌毒素]]能治疗陰道痙攣，故此其已被加入部分陰道痙攣的治疗流程中<ref name="Comer">{{cite book | author = Ronald J. Comer | title = Fundamentals of Abnormal Psychology | publisher = Macmillan | page = 338 | year = 2010 | accessdate = 2014-12-06 | isbn = 1429216336 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=y-FUzkLQ7GsC&pg=PA338 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326131757/http://books.google.com/books?id=y-FUzkLQ7GsC&pg=PA338 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。使人感到痛苦或不舒服的性交亦可歸类为[[性交疼痛|性交疼痛]]<ref name="Goldman"/>。

約40％的男性自稱至少偶爾地会發生某種形式的[[勃起功能障礙|勃起功能障礙]]（ED）<ref name="Schouten">{{cite journal |vauthors=Schouten BW, Bohnen AM, Groeneveld FP, Dohle GR, Thomas S, Bosch JL | title = Erectile dysfunction in the community: trends over time in incidence, prevalence, GP consultation and medication use—the Krimpen study: trends in ED | journal = J Sex Med | volume = 7 | issue = 7 | pages = 2547–53 | date =2010-07 | pmid = 20497307 | doi = 10.1111/j.1743-6109.2010.01849.x }}</ref>。早發性射精比勃起功能障礙更為普遍，儘管各方估計不盡相同<ref name="Porst"/><ref name="Emmanuele"/><ref name="Schouten" />。由於研究者對早發性射精的定義不为一致，所以對其患病率的估計差異遠比勃起功能障礙的大<ref name="Porst" /><ref name="Emmanuele" />。例如[[马约诊所|马约诊所]]指出：「儘管估計有所不同，但3个男士中便有1个在某些時候可能會受到其（早發性射精）影響<ref name="Premature ejaculation">{{cite web |url=http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/premature-ejaculation/home/ovc-20264121 |title=Premature ejaculation |publisher=[[Mayo_Clinic|Mayo Clinic]].com |accessdate=2017-05-20 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161021183359/http://www.mayoclinic.org/diseases-conditions/premature-ejaculation/basics/definition/con-20031160 |archivedate=2016-10-21 }}</ref> 。」；此外「麥斯特與強生推測，早發性射精是最常見的性功能障礙，即使会为勃起困難尋求治療的男性較多……[因為]雖估計15％至20％的男性在控制早發性射精方面遇上一些困難，但当中大多數不認為這是需要人幫助的問題，許多女性亦難以表達自己的性需求<ref name="Reinisch"/>。」{{link-en|美国泌尿外科学会|American Urological Association}}估計有21％的美国男性受到早發性射精的影響<ref name="auanet.org">{{cite web |title=Guideline on the pharmacologic management of premature ejaculation |publisher=American Urological Association |year=2004 |accessdate=2013-10-12 |url=http://www.auanet.org/common/pdf/education/clinical-guidance/Premature-Ejaculation.pdf |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160303170443/http://www.auanet.org/common/pdf/education/clinical-guidance/Premature-Ejaculation.pdf |archivedate=2016-03-03 }}</ref>。

對於因生理疾病而併發勃起功能障礙的人而言，[[他达拉非|他达拉非]]、[[伐地那非|伐地那非]]、[[西地那非|西地那非]]（俗名偉哥）等处方藥都有助於其回復至足以進行性交的硬度，但是醫師們警告説不要非必要地使用這些藥物，因為它們伴有嚴重的副作用，比如令心臟病發作的风險增加<ref name="Greenberg ED">{{cite book |author= Jerrold S Greenberg |author2= Clint E. Bruess |author3= Dean Emeritus |title= Exploring the Dimensions of Human Sexuality |publisher= Jones & Bartlett Publishers |page= 633 |year= 2010 |accessdate= 2014-12-08 |isbn= 0763797405 |url= https://books.google.com/books?id=6b36v8JHznIC&pg=PA633 |archive-url= https://web.archive.org/web/20150326132422/http://books.google.com/books?id=6b36v8JHznIC&pg=PA633 |archive-date= 2015-03-26 |dead-url= no }}</ref>。[[选择性5-羟色胺再摄取抑制剂|选择性5-羟色胺再摄取抑制剂]]（SSRI）及[[達泊西汀|達泊西汀]]这类藥物已在早發性射精的治療中有所應用<ref name="Balon">{{cite book|author=Richard Balon|author2=Robert Taylor Segraves|title=Clinical Manual of Sexual Disorders|publisher=American Psychiatric Pub|page=292|year=2009|accessdate=2014-12-06|isbn=1585629057|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=YuP3Hb0TMLQC&pg=PA292|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326121307/http://books.google.com/books?id=YuP3Hb0TMLQC&pg=PA292|archive-date=2015-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。與没有服用任何药物时相比，服用達泊西汀的早發性射精患者在臨床性交試驗中花3-4倍时間才達至高潮<ref name="Architectural Press">{{cite book |title=The Architects' Journal |volume=221 |issue=17-21 |publisher=Architectural Press |page=16 |year=2005 |accessdate=2014-12-06 |url=https://books.google.com/books?id=7HlNAAAAYAAJ&q=The+Architects%27+Journal,+Volume+221,+Issues+17-21&dq=The+Architects%27+Journal,+Volume+221,+Issues+17-21&hl=en&sa=X&ei=E8uDVKqUNM6sogTpz4G4BA&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAA |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326121818/http://books.google.com/books?id=7HlNAAAAYAAJ&q=The+Architects%27+Journal,+Volume+221,+Issues+17-21&dq=The+Architects%27+Journal,+Volume+221,+Issues+17-21&hl=en&sa=X&ei=E8uDVKqUNM6sogTpz4G4BA&ved=0CCgQ6AEwAA |archive-date=2015-03-26 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。[[迟泄|迟泄]]也是一种跟射精相关的障礙，它可由抗抑鬱藥物的副作用所導致，比如[[氟伏沙明|氟伏沙明]]；但所有SSRI型的抗抑鬱藥均具有延遲射精的副作用，氟伏沙明則是当中延遲效果最少的<ref name="Balon2">{{cite book | author = Richard Balon | author2 = Robert Taylor Segraves | title = Clinical Manual of Sexual Disorders | publisher = American Psychiatric Pub | page = 281 | year = 2009 | accessdate = 2014-12-06 | isbn = 1585629057 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=YuP3Hb0TMLQC&pg=PA281 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326124424/http://books.google.com/books?id=YuP3Hb0TMLQC&pg=PA281 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。

在對生殖器官及其某些構造進行大型的治疗后，当事人仍有很大机会可繼續从事性交，尤其是女性。許多婦科手術一般不会造成性交上的困難，比如[[子宮切除術|子宮切除術]]、{{link-en|卵巢切除術|oophorectomy}}、[[輸卵管切除術|輸卵管切除術]]、{{link-en|子宮擴刮術|Dilation and curettage}}、{{link-en|处女膜切开术|Hymenotomy}}、跟[[前庭大腺|前庭大腺]]有关的手術、膿腫切除術、前庭切除術、[[小陰唇|陰唇]]縮小術、{{link-en|子宮頸錐狀切除術|Cervical conization}}、治療癌症的外科手術、放射治療和化療<ref name="Hoffman2012">{{cite book | last = Hoffman | first = Barbara | title = Williams gynecology | edition = 2nd | publisher = McGraw-Hill Medical |page=65 |location = New York | year = 2012 | isbn = 0071716726 }}</ref>。

===其他障礙的影響===
[[身心障礙|身心障礙]]者在從事性交时可能面臨各种各样的挑戰及困難，包括疼痛、[[抑鬱|抑鬱]]、疲勞、負面的[[身體意象|身體意象]]、性功能障礙、焦慮、性欲低下、體內激素失衡，以及藥物治療的副作用。[[類風濕性關節炎|類風濕性關節炎]]患者的性功能對生活質量的影響通常遭到忽視<ref name="Tristano2014">{{cite journal|last1=Tristano|first1=Antonio G|title=Impact of rheumatoid arthritis on sexual function|journal=World Journal of Orthopedics|volume=5|issue=2|year=2014|page=107|issn=2218-5836|doi=10.5312/wjo.v5.i2.107}}</ref>。對於那些必須以鴉片類藥物控制疼痛的患者而言，性交通常會變得較難去实行<ref name="DeyoVon Korff2015">{{cite journal|last1=Deyo|first1=R. A.|last2=Von Korff|first2=M.|last3=Duhrkoop|first3=D.|title=Opioids for low back pain|journal=BMJ|volume=350|issue=jan05 10|year=2015|pages=g6380–g6380|issn=1756-1833|doi=10.1136/bmj.g6380}}</ref>。中風也可能会使当事人从事性交的能力大受影响<ref name="HersonPalmateer2012">{{cite journal|last1=Herson|first1=Paco S.|last2=Palmateer|first2=Julie|last3=Hurn|first3=Patricia D.|title=Biological Sex and Mechanisms of Ischemic Brain Injury|journal=Translational Stroke Research|volume=4|issue=4|year=2012|pages=413–419|issn=1868-4483|doi=10.1007/s12975-012-0238-x}}</ref>。雖然諸如行动障碍和癌症般的身心障礙所引起的疼痛可能会使患者不能順利地完成性交，但身心障礙者的性交困難往往是心因性的<ref name="Falvo">{{cite book|author=Donna Falvo|title=Medical and Psychosocial Aspects of Chronic Illness and Disability|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Publishers|page=367|year=2013|accessdate=2014-12-07|isbn=144969442X|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=SdM6FsykfWAC&pg=PA367|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326125814/http://books.google.com/books?id=SdM6FsykfWAC&pg=PA367|archive-date=2015-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。他們可能会對性交感到害怕，這可歸因於性的自我形象、伴侶以及自己的不安<ref name="Falvo"/>。当某人飲用大量酒精飲料时，其可能會出現暫时性的性交困難。因為酒精最初会以去除對行为的抑制力的方式，把性欲增加；但一旦攝取量增加，当事人便可能会失去性交能力<ref name="WHO Risks">{{cite book|title=Alcohol Use and Sexual Risk Behaviour: A Cross-cultural Study in Eight Countries|publisher=[[World_Health_Organization|World Health Organization]]|year=2005|pages=135|accessdate=2013-03-30|isbn=9241562897|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=fZ1eBPIIr48C|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140108014021/http://books.google.com/books?id=fZ1eBPIIr48C|archive-date=2014-01-08|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="Aggleton">{{cite book|author=Peter Aggleton|author2=Andrew Ball|author3=Purnima Mane|title=Sex, Drugs and Young People: International Perspectives|publisher=[[Routledge|Routledge]]|pages=130–133|year=2013|accessdate=2014-12-07|isbn=1134333099|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dWknAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA130|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150326124617/http://books.google.com/books?id=dWknAAAAQBAJ&pg=PA130|archive-date=2015-03-26|dead-url=no}}</ref>。

{{link-en|智能低下|Developmental disability}}者從事性交时也有可能面臨挑戰。有智力障礙的女性通常在性交時會遇到一些困难，主要原因包括为智力障礙者提供相关教育的尃業醫療人員過少。智力障礙者可能對性問題的討論顯得犹豫，他們的性知識普遍缺乏，接受性教育的機會也十分有限。此外还有其他会影響他们從事性交的障礙，比如智力障礙者遭性侵和性虐的机会較高，但只有少部分案件受到舉發。社会對「這类人群的性表達权利、月经失调的處理方法，以及相关保障法律」仍然缺乏共识。有智力障礙的女性可能缺乏接受性教育的機會，以及性健康保健知识。他們可能不能夠了解什麼是「性虐待」。一些智力障礙者並不具備「同意進行性交」的能力，因为他們對性交的了解可能十分有限，且欠缺获取避孕器具、篩查性傳染病/子宮頸癌的途徑及知識<ref name="GreenwoodWilkinson2013">{{cite journal|last1=Greenwood|first1=Nechama W.|last2=Wilkinson|first2=Joanne|title=Sexual and Reproductive Health Care for Women with Intellectual Disabilities: A Primary Care Perspective|journal=International Journal of Family Medicine|volume=2013|year=2013|pages=1–8|issn=2090-2042|doi=10.1155/2013/642472}}</ref>。

==對特定群體的影響==
===成年人===
諸如{{link-en|艾力克·康弗|Alex Comfort}}般的研究者假設道人類性行為有三項潛在且不互相排斥的好處/功能：生育、维持關係以及享樂<ref name="Diamond"/><ref name="Comfort">{{cite book|last=Comfort|first=Alex|title=The New Joy of Sex: A Gourmet Guide to Lovemaking|publisher=Diane Publishing Company|year=1991|pages=253 pages|accessdate=2013-08-16|isbn=0756783526|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=nfijPQAACAAJ|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143546/http://books.google.com/books?id=nfijPQAACAAJ|archive-date=2013-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。雖因避孕方法在20世紀中葉至20世紀晚期不斷進步的關係，使人們分離這三大功能的能力得以增加，但它們仍然顯著複雜地交織在一起。比如一對富生育能力的伴侣虽可能會發生有採取避孕方法的性交，但不全是為了體驗性愉悅（享樂），還以其作為维持情感親密的手段（维持關係），繼使他們的感情紐帶加深，以及使他們之間的关系更為穩定，还使得他們在未來更为有能力时才養育孩子（推迟生育）。时机的改變亦可能影響這對伴侣強調性交的哪一方面：有些時候所進行的性交可能強調一起共樂（享樂）；但在另一些時候會強調深層的感情聯繫（维持關係）；停止避孕後所進行的性交則較強調實現懷孕（生育，或生育和维持關係皆有）<ref name="Comfort"/>。

由於缺乏性交而引起的[[性挫折|性饑渴]]會使離婚或關係破裂的風險增加，特別是男方的性饑渴<ref name="Munck">{{cite book | author = Victor C. De Munck | title = Romantic Love and Sexual Behavior: Perspectives from the Social Sciences | publisher = Greenwood Publishing Group | year = 1998 | pages = 148–149 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | isbn = 0275957268 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=I78VnFoINgQC&pg=PA148 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326124535/http://books.google.com/books?id=I78VnFoINgQC&pg=PA148 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Howe">{{cite book | author = Tasha R. Howe | title = Marriages and Families in the 21st Century: A Bioecological Approach | publisher = John Wiley & Sons | year = 2011 | page = 411 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | isbn = 1405195010 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=UHaLL0pYwhMC&pg=PA411 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326124910/http://books.google.com/books?id=UHaLL0pYwhMC&pg=PA411 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Fine">{{cite book | author1 = Mark A Fine | author2 = John H. Harvey | title = Handbook of Divorce and Relationship Dissolution | publisher = Psychology Press | year = 2013 | page = 160 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | isbn = 1317824210 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=wGZlAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA160 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326130921/https://books.google.com/books?id=wGZlAgAAQBAJ&pg=PA160 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。然而有些研究表明，如果已婚女士跟另一位男性一起調情/帶情欲地親吻/關係變得浪漫/發生性行為（[[外遇|外遇]]），那麼該名妻子的丈夫一般便會感到不滿<ref name="Munck"/><ref name="Howe"/>，特别是情緒較負面和綜合婚姻滿意度較低的男性<ref name="Fine"/>。其他研究報告亦指出因缺乏性交而導致離婚者並沒有佔很大比重，但其也是少部分离婚个案的根本原因<ref name="Reinisch2">{{cite book| author = June M. Reinisch| author2 = Ruth Beasley| title = The Kinsey Institute New Report On Sex| publisher = Macmillan| year = 1991| page = 74| accessdate = 2014-12-09| isbn = 0312063865| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=KsW6wPiXEd0C&pg=PA74| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326132510/http://books.google.com/books?id=KsW6wPiXEd0C&pg=PA74| archive-date = 2015-03-26| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Schwartz2">{{cite book | author = Pepper Schwartz | author2 = Virginia Rutter | title = The Gender of Sexuality | publisher = Rowman & Littlefield | year = 1998 | page = 129 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | isbn = 0803990421 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=7bWlvcpYGUcC&pg=PA129 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326120451/https://books.google.com/books?id=7bWlvcpYGUcC&pg=PA129 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。根據2010年的美國性健康與行為調查，與上一次性交是跟沒有任何關係的伴侶進行的男性相比，跟有關係的伴侶進行性交者在過程中的性喚醒水平較高、更为享受、擁有更少的勃起和性高潮問題，以及所感到的疼痛亦同樣較少<ref name="Yarber">{{cite book| author = William Yarber| author2 = Barbara Sayad| author3 = Bryan Strong| title = Human Sexuality: Diversity in Contemporary America| edition = Eighth| publisher = McGraw-Hill Higher Education| year = 2012| page = 445| accessdate = 2014-12-09| isbn = 0077435257| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=EWz7twAACAAJ&dq=Human+Sexuality:+Diversity+in+Contemporary+America&hl=en&sa=X&ei=0JuHVNbLLc3coATiyoKYCA&ved=0CB8Q6AEwAA| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326132922/https://books.google.com/books?id=EWz7twAACAAJ&dq=Human+Sexuality:+Diversity+in+Contemporary+America&hl=en&sa=X&ei=0JuHVNbLLc3coATiyoKYCA&ved=0CB8Q6AEwAA| archive-date = 2015-03-26| dead-url = no}}</ref>。

對於女性而言，她們往往会因配偶缺乏性方面的自发性而感到不滿。她們的性活動減少的原因可能是不能保持自身的吸引力、会妨礙性伴侶進行性交的健康問題<ref name="Montemurro">{{cite book | author = Beth Montemurro | title = Deserving Desire: Women's Stories of Sexual Evolution | publisher = Rutgers University Press | year = 2014 | page = 169 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | isbn = 0813573068 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=1XVYBQAAQBAJ&pg=PT169 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326121526/http://books.google.com/books?id=1XVYBQAAQBAJ&pg=PT169 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。一些女性表示她們最滿意的性經驗是跟別人有接觸交流的，此一聲稱一般不僅考慮對高潮的滿意度而作出<ref name="Wincze"/><ref name="Gurian">{{cite book | author = Michael Gurian | title = The Wonder of Aging: A New Approach to Embracing Life After Fifty | publisher = [[Simon_&_Schuster|Simon & Schuster]] | year = 2013 | page = 178 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | isbn = 1476706719 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=XyS5ebuXJWgC&pg=PT178 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326130419/https://books.google.com/books?id=XyS5ebuXJWgC&pg=PT178 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。若丈夫發生了[[一夜情|一夜情]]或多次不忠，身處於高衝突婚姻的妻子更有可能会選擇離婚<ref name="Fine"/>。

另外有研究表明，[[同居|同居]]的非婚伴侶進行性交的頻率比已婚夫婦的多，且更有可能從事該段關係以外的性活動，这可由[[蜜月|蜜月期]]現象來解釋（跟伴侣一起从事的性交的新奇性）；通常情況下，一對夫婦結婚的時間越長，性交的頻率便愈少——夫婦平均每週進行1-2次的性交/其他性活動，或大约每月6-7次<ref name="Strong2">{{cite book | author = Bryan Strong | author2 = Theodore Cohen | title = The Marriage and Family Experience: Intimate Relationships in a Changing Society | publisher = Cengage Learning | year = 2013 | page = 212 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | isbn = 1285531892 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=6ZIWAAAAQBAJ&pg=PT237 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326125949/https://books.google.com/books?id=6ZIWAAAAQBAJ&pg=PT237 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。年齡亦是性交頻率的影響因子，相對於年輕人，較年老的人从事性交的頻率較少<ref name="Strong2"/>。

===青少年===
青少年通常為了维持關係和享樂而進行性交，它可能對他們的生活產生負面或積極的影響。例如青少年懷孕可能在某些文化中受到美化，但在普遍社会中都會受到批评。研究表明{{link-en|青春期過早來臨|Precocious puberty}}（早熟）會使當事人擁有「要像成年人一樣行事」的壓力，即使他的情緒或認知还未成熟及完全<ref name="sex lives3">{{cite book | title=The Sex Lives of Teenagers| url=https://archive.org/details/sexlivesofteenag00pont| isbn=978-0-452-28260-5| last=Ponton| first=Lynn| year=2000| page=[https://archive.org/details/sexlivesofteenag00pont/page/3 3]| publisher=Dutton Publishing}}</ref>。一些研究的結論認為從事性交會使青少年的壓力和抑鬱水平上升，尤其是青少女；青少女更有可能會進行高危的性行為（比如不使用避孕套的性交）<ref name="DiClemente">{{cite book| author = Ralph J. DiClemente| author2 = John S. Santelli| author3 = Richard A. Crosby| title = Adolescent Health: Understanding and Preventing Risk Behaviors| publisher = John Wiley & Sons| year = 2009| pages = 521–522| accessdate = 2014-12-07| isbn = 047045279X| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=KcrwY8eCwcQC&pg=PT521| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326132937/http://books.google.com/books?id=KcrwY8eCwcQC&pg=PT521| archive-date = 2015-03-26| dead-url = no}}</ref><ref name="Abaied">{{cite book| author = Jamie L Abaied| author2 = Deepika Anand| author3 = Tracey L Auster| author4 = Daniel BE| title = The Oxford Handbook of Depression and Comorbidity| publisher = [[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]]| year = 2014| page = 450| accessdate = 2014-12-07| isbn = 0199797005| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=hzpsAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA450| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326133507/http://books.google.com/books?id=hzpsAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA450| archive-date = 2015-03-26| dead-url = no}}</ref>，但此一範疇可能需要更進一步的研究<ref name="Abaied"/>。一些國家會以[[守貞教育|守貞教育]]以及[[性教育|性教育]]來教導青少年有關性活動的知識，比如美國。這些課程是帶爭議性的，比如「是否只應留给父母或監護人教導兒童和青少年有關性交或其他性活動的知識？」此一問題就已有爭議<ref name="Ryan">{{cite book| author =Kevin Ryan| author2 =James Cooper| title =Those Who Can, Teach| publisher =Cengage Learning| year =2008| page =110| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =0547204884| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=rqmdR6Xrgq8C&pg=PA110| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326133508/https://books.google.com/books?id=rqmdR6Xrgq8C&pg=PA110| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref>。

一些在20世纪70年代至90年代進行的研究顯示，對於青少年而言，性交跟[[自尊|自尊]]是有關係的<ref name="Lerner 2">{{cite book | authors = Richard M. Lerner, Daniel F. Perkins | title = Social Interactions in Adolescence and Promoting Positive Social Contributions of Youth | publisher = Taylor & Francis | year = 1999 | page = 124 | accessdate = 2017-04-14 | isbn = 0815332955 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=BunEIQylaJAC&pg=PA124 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170415112552/https://books.google.com/books?id=BunEIQylaJAC&pg=PA124 | archive-date = 2017-04-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但是其他在20世纪80年代至90年代進行的研究則表示，性交跟自尊在總體上只有很少關係，或根本沒有關係<ref name=" Kowalski">{{cite book| authors = Robin M. Kowalski, Mark R. Leary| title = The Interface of Social and Clinical Psychology: Key Readings| publisher = Psychology Press| year = 2004| page = 121| accessdate = 2017-04-17| isbn = 1841690872| url = https://books.google.com/books?id=qkEdaQ4heGgC&pg=PA121| archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170415112728/https://books.google.com/books?id=qkEdaQ4heGgC&pg=PA121| archive-date = 2017-04-15| dead-url = no}}</ref>。到了90年代，證據一般都是支持後者<ref name="Kowalski"/>，更進一步的研究亦同樣指出性交跟自尊只有很少關係，或根本沒有關係<ref name="Guindon">{{cite book| author =Mary H. Guindon| title =Self-Esteem Across the Lifespan: Issues and Interventions| publisher =Taylor & Francis| year =2009| page =147| accessdate =2017-04-14| isbn =1841690872| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=EcoPo06GYCMC&pg=PA147| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20170415112010/https://books.google.com/books?id=EcoPo06GYCMC&pg=PA147| archive-date =2017-04-15| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name="Lisa Arai">{{cite book | author = Lisa Arai | title = Teenage Pregnancy: The Making and Unmaking of a Problem | publisher = Policy Press | year = 2009 | page = 147 | accessdate = 2017-04-14 | isbn = 1847420745 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=qzOguz7GqNoC&pg=PA32 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170415111610/https://books.google.com/books?id=qzOguz7GqNoC&pg=PA32 | archive-date = 2017-04-15 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。麗莎·阿雷（Lisa Arai）這名學者指出：「『較早的性活動和懷孕跟自尊过低有关』的觀念在20世紀後半葉開始進入主流，特別是美國……一份關於自尊與青少年性行為、性態度、性意愿之間的關係的系統評價發現，62％的行為調查和72％的態度調查顯示兩者毫無統計學意義（Goodson et al，2006）<ref name="Lisa Arai"/>。」但亦有研究發現不是童貞的少男的自尊心高於還是童貞的；[[自我意象|自我意象]]差且自尊心低的青少女更傾向於從事高風險行為，比如無進行任何保護的性行為、擁有多個性夥伴<ref name="Lerner 2"/><ref name="Guindon"/><ref name="Lisa Arai"/> 。

心理學家{{link-en|林恩·龐頓|Lynn Ponton}}寫道：「所有青少年都有性生活，不論是跟他人還是自己進行的，遭認為沒有性經驗的青少年亦同樣如是。」她還把青少年的性行為視為一種可能會為當事人帶來正面影響的經驗，而不是固有觀念中的「危险事件」，她認為其可幫助年輕人發展得更健康，並對日後的性生活做出更積極的選擇<ref name="Madsen S., Collins W. A. 2005"/>。還有一些研究者指出長期的浪漫關係，能使青少年獲得維繫日後的高質量關係所必需的技能<ref name="Madsen S., Collins W. A. 2005">{{cite book|last1=Madsen|first1= S.|last2=Collins|first2= W. A.|year=2005 |chapter=Differential predictions of young adult romantic relationships from transitory vs. longer romantic experiences during adolescence|title=Biennial Meeting of the Society for Research on Child Development|location=Atlanta, Georgia}}</ref>。總體而言，青少年的積極浪漫關係可帶來長期的好處。高質量的浪漫關係亦與成年早期的高度献身有著關係<ref>{{cite book|last1=Seiffge-Krenke|first1=I.|last2=Lang|first2=J.|year=2002 |chapter=Forming and maintaining romantic relations from early adolescence to young adulthood: evidence of a developmental sequence|title=Biennial Meeting of the Society for Research on Adolescence|location=New Orleans, Louisiana}}</ref>，並跟社交能力正相關<ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Pearce MJ, Boergers J, Prinstein MJ | title = Adolescent obesity, overt and relational peer victimization, and romantic relationships | journal = Obesity Research | volume = 10 | issue = 5 | pages = 386–93 | year = 2002 | pmid = 12006638 | doi = 10.1038/oby.2002.53 | url =  }}</ref><ref>{{cite journal |vauthors=Zimmer-Gembeck MJ, Siebenbruner J, Collins WA | title = A prospective study of intraindividual and peer influences on adolescents' heterosexual romantic and sexual behavior | journal = Archives of Sexual Behavior | volume = 33 | issue = 4 | pages = 381–394 | year = 2004 | pmid = 15162084 | doi = 10.1023/B:ASEB.0000028891.16654.2c | url =https://archive.org/details/sim_archives-of-sexual-behavior_2004-08_33_4/page/381}}</ref>。

==道德、宗教和法律觀點==
{{See also|性倫理|宗教與性|性犯罪}}
[[File:Erotic_scenes_Louvre_G13_n4.jpg|thumb]]]]
雖然性交是人類繁殖後代的自然狀態，但人類具有規範性行為的道德倫理標準，那些標準往往是復雜的，並會受到宗教和法律的影響而變化。某些政府和宗教也嚴格規定了哪種性行為屬「適當」，哪種屬「不適當」。肛交在歷史上曾遭禁止或受到管制<ref>{{cite book|author=William N. Eskridge Jr.|title= Dishonorable Passs: Sodomy Laws in America, 1861–2003|url=https://archive.org/details/dishonorablepass00eskr|year=2008|publisher=Viking Adult|isbn=0-670-01862-7}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|author=Noelle N. R. Quenivet|title=Sexual Offenses in Armed Conflict & International Law|year=2005|publisher=Hotei Publishing|isbn=1-57105-341-7}}</ref>。

===性犯罪 ===
未經當事人[[性同意|同意]]或違背當事人意願的性交一般稱為[[强奸|强奸]]，但亦可稱為[[性侵犯|性侵犯]]，强奸在大多數國家都會遭認定為嚴重[[罪行|罪行]]<ref name="Sex and Society">{{cite book | author = Marshall Cavendish Corporation | title = Sex and Society | publisher = Marshall Cavendish Corporation | year = 2010 | pages = 143–144 | accessdate = 2013-08-25 | isbn = 0-7614-7906-6 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=aVDZchwkIMEC&lpg=PA143 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143600/http://books.google.com/books?id=aVDZchwkIMEC&lpg=PA143 | archive-date = 2013-12-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Greenberg2">{{cite book|author=Jerrold S. Greenberg|author2=Clint E. Bruess|author3=Sarah C. Conklin|title=Exploring the Dimensions of Human Sexuality|publisher=Jones & Bartlett Learning|year=2010|page=515|accessdate=2013-08-25|isbn=0-7637-7660-2|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=1NC5R0RozBYC&lpg=PA515|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143555/http://books.google.com/books?id=1NC5R0RozBYC&lpg=PA515|archive-date=2013-12-31|dead-url=no}}</ref>。超過90％的強姦受害者是女性，99％的強姦犯是男性，只有約5％的強姦犯是受害者不認識的<ref name="Greenberg2"/>。

大多數已發展國家都設有[[最低合法性交年齡|最低合法性交年齡]]限制。規定了當事人進行性交的最低合法年齡。最低合法性交年齡通常為16-18歲，但其範圍可延伸至12-20歲，一些文化的最低性交年齡是依據非成文的習俗或傳統而定<ref name="Kinnear">{{cite book | author = Karen L. Kinnear | title = Childhood Sexual Abuse: A Reference Handbook | publisher = ABC-CLIO | year = 2007 | page = 89 | accessdate = 2013-08-25 | isbn = 1-85109-905-0 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=V1rogCrcOMwC&printsec=frontcover&dq=&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9iFlUqmkE4e_2QX_84GgBA&ved=0CEoQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=&f=false | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231223642/http://books.google.com/books?id=V1rogCrcOMwC&printsec=frontcover&dq=&hl=en&sa=X&ei=9iFlUqmkE4e_2QX_84GgBA&ved=0CEoQ6AEwAA#v=onepage&q=&f=false | archive-date = 2013-12-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。不論當事人是否同意，與低於合法年齡的人所進行的性交，都會遭認定為性侵犯或法定強姦（視乎參與者的年齡差異而決定採用何者）。某些國家把任何與精神能力不足以「同意進行性交」者發生的性行為定為強姦，不論年齡性別<ref>{{cite journal |last=Reed|first=E. J.|title=Criminal Law and the Capacity of Mentally Retarded Persons to Consent to Sexual Activity |journal=Virginia Law Review |year=1997|volume= 83|issue=4 |pages=799–827|jstor=1073749|doi=10.2307/1073749}}</ref>。此法律的設立目的之一是為了保護兒少免受性侵或性剝削<ref>{{cite news|title=法改會推諮詢　倡最低合法性交年齡劃一16歲|url=http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161101/bkn-20161101150007807-1101_00822_001.html|publisher=東方日報|date=2016-11-01|accessdate=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723122525/http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20161101/bkn-20161101150007807-1101_00822_001.html|archive-date=2018-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="性自主權">{{cite news|title=為什麼用法律剝奪「性自主權」？|url=https://opinion.udn.com/opinion/story/6070/1294377|publisher=鳴人堂|date=2015-11-05|accessdate=2018-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180723122515/https://opinion.udn.com/opinion/story/6070/1294377|archive-date=2018-07-23|dead-url=no}}</ref>，但亦有觀點認為其剝奪了未成年人的[[性權|性權利]]<ref>{{cite journal|author1=趙合俊|author2=方剛|title=嫖宿幼女案及取消嫖宿幼女罪的爭議|journal=華人性權研究|url=http://www.wacshome.net/china/CSRR_2.pdf|issue=2|date=2010-03-01|page=25|accessdate=2018-07-23|author=|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20111010075836/http://www.wacshome.net/china/CSRR_2.pdf|archive-date=2011-10-10|dead-url=yes}}</ref><ref name="潘绥铭 性权利">{{cite web|title=性权利，该有年龄界限吗？|author=潘绥铭|url=http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4dd47e5a0102vrkx.html|date=2015-09-17|accessdate=2018-09-01|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20180901182634/http://blog.sina.com.cn/s/blog_4dd47e5a0102vrkx.html|archive-date=2018-09-01|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="性自主權"/>。性學家潘绥铭認為類似的規定應「因人而异地立法与执法」<ref name="潘绥铭 性权利"/>。
