羅伯特·弗朗科耶（Robert Francoeur）等人指出：「在20世紀70年代以前，只有陰莖－陰道交才会遭視作強姦<ref name="Francoeur">{{cite book | title = The Continuum Complete International Encyclopedia of Sexuality | publisher = Continuum International Publishing Group | year = 2004 | page = 173 | accessdate = 2013-04-30 | isbn = 0826414885 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=PQMTzc6y8ZAC&pg=PA173 | author1 = Robert T. Francoeur | author2 = Raymond J. Noonan | author3 = Beldina Opiyo-Omolo | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20131231143833/http://books.google.com/books?id=PQMTzc6y8ZAC&pg=PA173 | archive-date = 2013-12-31 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。」帕梅拉·卡爾布弗萊施（Pamela J. Kalbfleisch）和迈克尔·科迪（Michael J.Cody）表示這種看法是基於：「性行為只等同於陰莖－陰道交的想法；以此為基礎推論下去的話，強姦即等同強迫對方進行的陰莖－陰道交。而諸如強迫口交和同性脅迫般的性侵害行為，則因此不被視作強姦……儘管其他形式的強迫性接觸會依法定為[[性悖軌|性悖軌]]（例如肛交、口腔－生殖器接觸），但是在美國某些州的法律中，許多当事人不願意發生的性接觸都不被視作強姦<ref name="Kalbfleisch"/>。」Ken Plumber同樣指出：「大多數國家的法律把強奸定為非法的性交合。換句話說，陰莖必須跟陰道互相接合才会符合以上定義……其他針對女性的性暴力只会構成『不太嚴重』的性侵罪，例如強迫口交/肛交/插入其他東西至陰道<ref name="Plummer"/>。」

隨著時間的推移，某些國家及地區對於強奸的定義亦已延伸了不少，當中已包含各種類型的性侵入行為，比如肛交、口交、舔陰，以及把死物插入至生殖器或直腸<ref name="Francoeur"/>。2012年以前，[[聯邦調查局|美國聯邦調查局]]（FBI）仍認為強姦只是男人對女性進行的犯罪行為。但在2012年他們對於強奸的定義已從「強迫該名女性進行，且違背她意志的性行為」改為「沒得到受害者同意而進行的性行為，包括不論多麼輕微的陰道或肛門侵入、把性器官插入口腔。」該定義并不對聯邦或州的刑法典，或聯邦、州或地方層面的起訴作出任何改動，卻使得美國的強姦案例能更準確地如实反映<ref>{{cite news |url=https://www.nytimes.com/2012/01/07/us/politics/federal-crime-statistics-to-expand-rape-definition.html |title=U.S. to Expand Rape Definition in Crime Statistics |publisher=New York Times |date=2012-01-06 |accessdate=2017-05-22 |author=Charlie Savage |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20120107021022/https://www.nytimes.com/2012/01/07/us/politics/federal-crime-statistics-to-expand-rape-definition.html |archivedate=2012-01-07 }}</ref>。没有任何性侵入的強迫性接觸在某些情況下亦會界定為強奸<ref name="Book04">{{cite book|last=Smith|first=ed. by Merril D.|title=Encyclopedia of rape|url=https://archive.org/details/encyclopediarape00smit_435|year=2004|publisher=Greenwood Press|location=Westport, Conn. [u.a.]|isbn=978-0-313-32687-5|pages=[https://archive.org/details/encyclopediarape00smit_435/page/n190 169]–170|edition=1. publ.}}</ref>。

在部份文化中將[[近親性交|近親間的性交]]視為[[亂倫|亂倫]]，且視之為罪行。[[蒙纳士大学|蒙纳士大学]]犯罪學高級講師詹姆斯·羅夫（James Roffee）曾聯同一名在英國、威爾士以及蘇格蘭工作的前家庭性活動法应对者<ref>{{cite web |url=http://monash.edu/research/explore/en/persons/james-roffee(896c15d7-6f28-4bf0-8a0f-b7d6ff1553e0).html |title=Dr James Roffee |publisher=Monash university |accessdate=2017-05-22 |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170204003059/http://monash.edu/research/explore/en/persons/james-roffee%28896c15d7-6f28-4bf0-8a0f-b7d6ff1553e0%29.html |archivedate=2017-02-04 }}</ref>，一同探討跟近亲性活動有關的潛在危害，比如容易産生有成長缺陷的後代。然而，法律更關心的是可能在當中遭受近亲虐待的人的權利，並予以適當條文保護——这就是不論當事人是否自願發生近親性交，一概認定为違法之原因。但香港性教育促進會副主席[[吳敏倫|吳敏倫]]則反指近親性交並不一定是為了生育，且法律沒有禁止患遺傳病的人結婚生子，所以「容易産生有成長缺陷的後代」的論據不合理<ref>{{cite news|title=【成年人近親性交】吳敏倫倡廢亂倫罪　何君堯斥違家庭觀、同運致亂倫|url=https://thestandnews.com/society/成年人近親性交-吳敏倫倡廢亂倫罪-何君堯斥違家庭觀-同運致亂倫/|publisher=立場新聞|date=2017-05-16|accessdate=2017-09-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170714211139/http://thestandnews.com/society/%E6%88%90%E5%B9%B4%E4%BA%BA%E8%BF%91%E8%A6%AA%E6%80%A7%E4%BA%A4-%E5%90%B3%E6%95%8F%E5%80%AB%E5%80%A1%E5%BB%A2%E4%BA%82%E5%80%AB%E7%BD%AA-%E4%BD%95%E5%90%9B%E5%A0%AF%E6%96%A5%E9%81%95%E5%AE%B6%E5%BA%AD%E8%A7%80-%E5%90%8C%E9%81%8B%E8%87%B4%E4%BA%82%E5%80%AB/|archive-date=2017-07-14|dead-url=no}}</ref>；而遭受近亲虐待的人亦可按其他法律處理<ref>{{cite web|title=吳敏倫︰齊來理性 2018-6-15 擴大亂倫罪？|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=abj9IKgg81o|date=2018-06-14|accessdate=2018-06-15|archive-date=2021-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210723024140/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=abj9IKgg81o|dead-url=no}}</ref>。此外有些地區的法律禁止親屬之間的各種性行為，包括但不限于帶侵入成份的。相关法律所指的「近亲」一般包括祖父母、父母、子女、兄弟姐妹、伯叔舅嬸姨姑。但「近亲」的定義以及懲罰的嚴重程度會因國家及地區而異，「近亲」的定義可能包括，也可能不包括生物学上的父母、繼父母、養父母、异父同胞<ref>{{cite journal|last=Roffee|first=J. A.|title=No Consensus on Incest? Criminalisation and Compatibility with the European Convention on Human Rights|journal=Human Rights Law Review|volume=14|issue=3|url=https://academic.oup.com/hrlr/article/14/3/541/644298/No-Consensus-on-Incest-Criminalisation-and|doi=10.1093/hrlr/ngu023|date=2014-07-23|pages=541-72}}</ref>。

另一項關於「同意」與否的性事就是[[動物戀|動物戀]]，指的一般是人與動物之間所發生的性行為，但亦可指對相关实踐的执着，屬[[性偏離|性偏離]]的一种<ref name="DSM">{{cite book |title=Diagnostic and Statistical Manual of Mental Disorders: DSM-IV | publisher = [[American_Psychiatric_Association|American Psychiatric Association]] | location=Washington, DC |year=2000 |pages= |isbn=0-89042-025-4 |oclc= |doi=}}</ref><ref name="Milner2008">{{cite book | veditors = Laws DR, O'Donohue WT | last-author-amp = yes | last = Milner | first = JS | author2 = Dopke CA | title = Sexual Deviance, Second Edition: Theory, Assessment, and Treatment | publisher = The Guilford Press | location = New York | year = 2008 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=yIXG9FuqbaIC&pg=PA385 | pages = 384–418 | isbn = 1-59385-605-9 | oclc =  | doi =  | chapter = Paraphilia Not Otherwise Specified: Psychopathology and theory | access-date = 2017-05-01 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20170305182924/https://books.google.com/books?id=yIXG9FuqbaIC&pg=PA385 | archive-date = 2017-03-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Seto2000">{{cite book |editor = Hersen M |editor2 = Van Hasselt VB | title = Aggression and violence: an introductory text |publisher= Allyn & Bacon |location=Boston |year=2000 |pages= 198–213 |isbn=0-205-26721-1 |oclc= |doi=| last = Seto| first = MC|author2=Barbaree HE  | chapter = Paraphilias}}</ref>。在某些司法管轄區，某人與非人動物發生性行為不屬違法，但在其他地区，則会遭視为違反[[虐待動物|虐待動物]]法，或是干犯了{{link-en|违反自然罪|crime against nature}}<ref name="Perdue">{{cite book| author =Abigail Perdue| author2 =Randall Lockwood| title =Animal Cruelty and Freedom of Speech: When Worlds Collide| publisher =Purdue University Press| year =2014| pages =6–8| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =1557536333| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=R1ncAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA6| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326113418/https://books.google.com/books?id=R1ncAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA6| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref>。支持訂立相關法律的人所提出的理由包括「獸交對動物是有害的」<ref name=Regan63>{{cite book|last=Regan|first=Tom|title=Animal Rights, Human Wrongs|url=https://archive.org/details/animalrightshuma0000rega|publisher =Rowman & Littlefield| year = 2003|pages = [https://archive.org/details/animalrightshuma0000rega/page/63 63]–4, 89}}</ref>、「動物無法表達同意與否」<ref name=Regan63/>、「[獸交]有違人的基本尊嚴」<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.weeklystandard.com/article/7184|title=Horse Sense|publisher=Weeklystandard.com|date=2005-08-31}}{{Dead link|date=2020年1月 |bot=InternetArchiveBot |fix-attempted=yes }}</ref>。反對訂立者所提出的理由則包括「人類既然可以殺死動物並吃之，那麼禁止人獸交已在邏輯上說不通」<ref>{{cite news|title=吴敏伦：人可以杀动物 为什么不能人兽性交|url=http://phtv.ifeng.com/program/qqsrx/detail_2012_01/29/12167865_0.shtml|accessdate=2017-09-04|date=2012-01-29|publisher=凤凰网|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170904155203/http://phtv.ifeng.com/program/qqsrx/detail_2012_01/29/12167865_0.shtml|archive-date=2017-09-04|dead-url=no}}</ref>、「吃動物也侵犯了人及動物的尊嚴」<ref>{{cite web|title=吳敏倫︰齊來理性 2018-7-13 獸交|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hAtmYhCbrlg|date=2018-07-13|access-date=2018-07-14|archive-date=2021-07-23|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20210723021031/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=hAtmYhCbrlg|dead-url=no}}</ref>、「動物可以某些方式表達同意」<ref>{{cite journal|last=Miletski|first=Hani|title=Bestiality – Zoophilia: An exploratory study|journal=The Institute for Advanced Study of Human Sexuality|year=1999|volume=3|pages=149-150}}</ref>。

===浪漫關係===
====婚姻關係====
性交在傳統上往往遭視為婚姻的重要組成部分，許多宗教習俗都會要求当事人在成婚后[[洞房|洞房]]，把有性生殖視為婚姻最適合的證明及結合<ref name="Hogan">{{cite book| author =Margaret Monahan Hogan| title =Marriage as a Relationship: Real and Rational| publisher =Marquette University Press| year =2002| page =88| accessdate =2015-09-01| isbn =0874626579| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=HuztAAAAMAAJ&q=Marriage+as+a+Relationship:+Real+and+Rational| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150905085534/https://books.google.com/books?id=HuztAAAAMAAJ&q=Marriage+as+a+Relationship:+Real+and+Rational| archive-date =2015-09-05| dead-url =no}}</ref>。在這種情況下，若因任何理由而洞房失敗，該婚事不需要任何離婚程序，即可視為无效。不論过去还是現在，在不同的社會和宗教中婚姻伴侶之間的性關係，一直視为「配偶應享有的權利」（marital right，亦稱婚姻权），尤其是指丈夫享有跟妻子發生性關係的權利<ref name="Dwyer">{{cite book | author = James G. Dwyer | title = Religious Schools V. Children's Rights | publisher = Cornell University Press | year = 2001 | pages = 72–73 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | isbn = 0801487315 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=QDwD4huqyysC&pg=PA72 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905082758/https://books.google.com/books?id=QDwD4huqyysC&pg=PA72 | archive-date = 2015-09-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Green">{{cite book | author = Ronald Green | title = Religion and Sexual Health: Ethical, Theological, and Clinical Perspectives, Volume 1 of Theology and Medicine | publisher = Springer Science & Business Media | year = 2013 | page = 112 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | isbn = 9401579636 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=h2mvBQAAQBAJ&pg=PT112 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905092237/https://books.google.com/books?id=h2mvBQAAQBAJ&pg=PT112 | archive-date = 2015-09-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Brook">{{cite book | author = Heather Brook | title = Conjugality: Marriage and Marriage-like Relationships Before the Law | publisher = Palgrave Macmillan | year = 2015 | pages = 71–73 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | isbn = 1137480912 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=rP2_CQAAQBAJ&pg=PA71 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905073629/https://books.google.com/books?id=rP2_CQAAQBAJ&pg=PA71 | archive-date = 2015-09-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。在20世紀後期以前，強姦法通常都豁免婚姻內的強奸，使得妻子不能以強姦法起訴強迫其進行性行為的丈夫<ref name="Steinmetz">{{cite book| author =Suzanne K. Steinmetz| author2 =Marvin B. Sussman| title =Handbook of Marriage and the Family| publisher =Springer Science & Business Media| year =2013| pages =787–788| accessdate =2014-08-31| isbn =1461571510| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=T6XwBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA787| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150905085902/https://books.google.com/books?id=T6XwBwAAQBAJ&pg=PA787| archive-date =2015-09-05| dead-url =no}}</ref>。Oshisanya和'lai Oshitokunbo在他們合著的著作中指出：「由於女性的法律地位已經改變，『配偶享有跟自己性交的權利』此一觀念已變得不那麽普遍<ref name="Oshitokunbo">{{cite book| author =Oshisanya, 'lai Oshitokunbo| title =An Almanac of Contemporary Judicial Restatements (Criminal & Quasi Criminal Law & Procedure) vol. iii: Almanac vol. iii| publisher =Almanac Foundation| year =2015| page =132| accessdate =2015-08-31| isbn =9785120031| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=fsDOBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA132| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150905082954/https://books.google.com/books?id=fsDOBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA132| archive-date =2015-09-05| dead-url =no}}</ref>。」

[[通奸|通奸]]（與婚姻以外者從事性交）在某些司法管轄區中依然是刑事罪行<ref name="Brundage">{{cite book | author = James A. Brundage | title = Law, Sex, and Christian Society in Medieval Europe | publisher = [[University_of_Chicago_Press|University of Chicago Press]] | year = 2009 | pages = 609–611 | accessdate = 2015-08-31 | isbn = 0226077896 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=SiGe-Zf0nTIC&pg=PA609 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905073726/https://books.google.com/books?id=SiGe-Zf0nTIC&pg=PA609 | archive-date = 2015-09-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref><ref name="Carlan">{{cite book| author =Philip Carlan| author2 =Lisa S. Nored| author3 =Ragan A. Downey| title =An Introduction to Criminal Law| publisher =Jones & Bartlett Publishers| year =2011| page =139| accessdate =2015-08-31| isbn =1449647219| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=8-tPwZyNWzkC&pg=PA139| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150905075332/https://books.google.com/books?id=8-tPwZyNWzkC&pg=PA139| archive-date =2015-09-05| dead-url =no}}</ref>。在某些司法管轄區，未婚伴侣的性交或同居也屬違法行為<ref name="BBC News">{{Cite news |title=Can Iran 'control' its cohabiting couples? |date=2014-12-10 |accessdate=2015-08-31 |publisher=BBC News |url=http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-30391593 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170218135318/http://www.bbc.com/news/world-middle-east-30391593 |archivedate=2017-02-18 }}</ref><ref name="amnesty.org">{{cite web |title=Amnesty International Report 2014/15 |date=2014 |accessdate=2015-08-31 |publisher=amnesty.org |url=https://www.amnesty.org/en/countries/middle-east-and-north-africa/morocco/report-morocco/ |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20170504233053/https://www.amnesty.org/en/countries/middle-east-and-north-africa/morocco/report-morocco/ |archivedate=2017-05-04 }}</ref>。在其他國家則相反——不需要婚姻基礎就可進行性交或繁殖下一代（比如说於冰島、挪威、瑞典、丹麥、保加利亞、愛沙尼亞、斯洛維尼亞、法國以及比利時產下孩子的母亲大多还没有结婚或已离婚）<ref name="europa.eu">{{cite web |title=Share of live births outside marriage |date=2015-03-02 |accessdate=2015-08-31 |publisher=europa.eu |url=http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/tgm/table.do?tab=table&plugin=1&language=en&pcode=tps00018 |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160527142604/http://ec.europa.eu/eurostat/tgm/table.do?tab=table&plugin=1&language=en&pcode=tps00018 |archivedate=2016-05-27 }}</ref>。

依据某些地區的離婚法，可以以拒絕與配偶進行性交為由申請离婚，並視作「因抛弃對方而離婚」（grounds of abandonment）<ref name=Choudhri>{{cite book| author =Choudhri, Nihara K| title =The complete guide to divorce law| publisher =New York: Citadel Press| year =2004| pages =8–9| accessdate =2015-08-30| isbn =0-8065-2528-2| url =https://books.google.com.au/books?id=5cLIO2yUA4gC&pg=PA8| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150905075338/https://books.google.com.au/books?id=5cLIO2yUA4gC&pg=PA8| archive-date =2015-09-05| dead-url =no}}</ref>。詹姆斯·德維爾（James G. Dwyer）在他的著作中指出設有{{link-en|無過錯離婚|no-fault divorce}}法能使「女性更輕易地从婚姻關係中脫離，並使妻子在婚姻中得到更多的控制权……這是『丈夫強姦妻子』的相关法律觀念改變所致<ref name="Dwyer"/>。」

不同法律對「同性/同[[社會性別|社會性別]]之間的性行為的定義和合法性」有着不同立場，比如於2003年進行裁決的大衛·布蘭奇福勞（David Blanchflower）申請跟西安·布蘭奇福勞（Sian Blanchflower）脫離婚姻關係一案中（他要求申請有過錯离婚，因為西安跟另一名女子發生性行為），{{link-en|新罕布什尔州最高法院|New Hampshire Supreme Court}}的法官根據1961年版的新韋氏國際字典的相關定義，認為女女性行為和同性性行為一般不能视为性交，因此判定妻子（被告）並没有犯下[[通姦|通姦]]的「過錯」<ref name="GLAD, B vs. B">{{cite web |title=Blanchflower v. Blanchflower and Mayer |publisher=Gay & Lesbian Advocates & Defenders (GLAD) |date=2003-12-31 |accessdate=2013-08-09 |url=http://www.glad.org/work/cases/blanchflower-v-blanchflower-and-mayer |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20161121174107/http://www.glad.org/work/cases/blanchflower-v-blanchflower-and-mayer |archivedate=2016-11-21 }}</ref><ref name="courts.state.nh.us">{{cite web |title=IN THE MATTER OF DAVID G. BLANCHFLOWER AND SIAN E. BLANCHFLOWER |publisher=New Hampshire Judicial Branch/courts.state.nh.us |date=2003-11-07 |accessdate=2013-08-09 |url=http://www.courts.state.nh.us/supreme/opinions/2003/blanc150.htm |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160910072202/http://www.courts.state.nh.us/supreme/opinions/2003/blanc150.htm |archivedate=2016-09-10 }}</ref>。有些國家認為同性性行為是可判處監禁或能處以極刑的罪行，比如屬[[LGBT與伊斯蘭教|伊斯蘭國家]]的[[伊朗LGBT權益|伊朗]]<ref>{{cite book|author=Janet Afary|title=Sexual Politics in Modern Iran|url=https://archive.org/details/sexualpoliticsin0000afar|year=2009|publisher =[[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]]|isbn =0-521-89846-3}}</ref><ref name="amnesty.org2">{{cite web |title=PUBLIC AI Index: MDE 13/010/2008. UA 17/08 Fear of imminent execution/ flogging |publisher=Amnesty International |accessdate=2013-12-22 |url=http://www2.amnesty.se/uaonnet.nsf/dfab8d7f58eec102c1257011006466e1/fd0b99f84da0da71c12573d7003a87a5?OpenDocument&Click= |deadurl=yes |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160305004923/http://www2.amnesty.se/uaonnet.nsf/dfab8d7f58eec102c1257011006466e1/fd0b99f84da0da71c12573d7003a87a5?OpenDocument&Click= |archivedate=2016-03-05 |df= }}</ref>。

====各宗教團體的看法====
各宗教團體對於婚内或婚外性交合有着不同的看法：

*包括[[天主教|天主教]]在內，[[基督教|基督教]]的大多數教派對於「可接受」和「不可接受」的性行為有着严格的觀點及規限<ref name="Akin">{{Cite book|author=Daniel L. Akin|title=God on Sex: The Creator's Ideas About Love, Intimacy, and Marriage|year=2003|publisher=B&H Publishing Group|pages=1–291|isbn=0805425969|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=dInbMZK18soC|accessdate=2015-10-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20150905091638/https://books.google.com/books?id=dInbMZK18soC|archive-date=2015-09-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。大多數基督教徒對性交的看法受到各種對《[[聖經|聖經]]》的演繹的影響<ref name="Hollinger">{{cite book | author = Dennis P. Hollinger | title = The Meaning of Sex: Christian Ethics and the Moral Life | publisher = Baker Academic | year = 2009 | pages = 30–33 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | isbn = 0801035716 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=86tzBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA30 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326124922/https://books.google.com/books?id=86tzBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA30 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。對於一些教派而言，婚外性交合本身就是一种[[罪_(宗教)|罪恶]]；在這種情況下，性交合可遭稱为丈夫與妻子之間的「終生聖約」和「圣礼」<ref name="Akin"/><ref name="Hollinger"/>。儘管基督教在歷史上一般會提倡人們終生守贞禁欲<ref name="Denton">{{cite book | author = Chad Denton | title = The War on Sex: Western Repression from the Torah to Victoria | publisher = [[McFarland_&_Company|McFarland]] | year = 2014 | pages = 107–117 | accessdate = 2014-12-09 | isbn = 0547204884 | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=Cl6QBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA107 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150326114101/https://books.google.com/books?id=Cl6QBQAAQBAJ&pg=PA107 | archive-date = 2015-03-26 | dead-url = no }}</ref>，但現今基本只有某些神職人員（例如宗教領袖）才會許下終生守贞的諾言，放棄婚姻和任何形式的性活動<ref name="Hollinger"/>。《聖經》的內容可遭解讀成只認定陰莖－陰道交为可接受的性行為<ref name="Kamitsuka">{{cite book| author =Margaret D. Kamitsuka| title =The Embrace of Eros: Bodies, Desires, and Sexuality in Christianity| publisher =Fortress Press| year =2010| pages =16–17| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =1451413513| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=VhIrHceA7ssC&pg=PA16| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326133528/https://books.google.com/books?id=VhIrHceA7ssC&pg=PA16| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name="Knauss">{{cite book| author =Stefanie Knauss| title =More Than a Provocation: Sexuality, Media and Theology| publisher =Vandenhoeck & Ruprecht| year =2014| page =69| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =3525604505| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=mv9NAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA69| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326124148/https://books.google.com/books?id=mv9NAwAAQBAJ&pg=PA69| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref>，而其他解讀則認为《聖經》並没有明確地提及口交或其他特定性行為，並認为婚内伴侣会否接受並進行「口交」完全纯屬个人的決定<ref name="Kamitsuka"/><ref name="Barnes">{{cite book| author =Robert G. Barnes| author2 =Rosemary J. Barnes| title =Great Sexpectations: Finding Lasting Intimacy in Your Marriage| publisher =Zondervan| year =1996| page =66| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =0310201373| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=LX8f73I7NTYC&pg=PA66| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326112045/https://books.google.com/books?id=LX8f73I7NTYC&pg=PA66| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name="Scheepers">{{cite book| author =Christo Scheepers| publisher =Struik Christian Media| title =Between the Covers: Sexual freedom through the bond of marriage| year =2012| page =53| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =141532056X| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=LJzpAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT53| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326132311/https://books.google.com/books?id=LJzpAwAAQBAJ&pg=PT53| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref>。一些教派認為使用他們所認定的「人工避孕法」來防止生育下一代屬嚴重罪恶，因為他們認為婚姻的主要目的，或其主要目的之一是生育子女，而其他教派則不具有這種信念<ref name="Oliphant">{{cite book | author = Jill Oliphant | title = OCR Religious Ethics for AS and A2 | publisher = [[Routledge|Routledge]] | year = 2010 | page = 213 | accessdate = 2015-09-01 | isbn = 113699291X | url = https://books.google.com/books?id=VmJd87byr1AC&pg=PT213 | archive-url = https://web.archive.org/web/20150905085505/https://books.google.com/books?id=VmJd87byr1AC&pg=PT213 | archive-date = 2015-09-05 | dead-url = no }}</ref>。《舊約聖經》曾禁止在[[月經|月經]]期間進行性交<ref name="Scheepers"/>。
**對於[[羅馬天主教會|羅馬天主教會]]而言，如果婚禮慶祝活動舉行過後，配偶未曾完成至少一次性交，那麼該段婚姻便可認定为未遂聖事婚姻。不論其聖事未遂的原因，只要其中一方申请，這樣的婚姻[[教宗|教宗]]是可以解除的，一旦教宗解除了該段婚姻，便代表該段婚姻從一開始就是無效的，即是在規範法中該對配偶末曾結婚<ref name="d'Avray">{{cite book| author =D. L. d'Avray| title =Rationalities in History: A Weberian Essay in Comparison| publisher =[[Cambridge_University_Press|Cambridge University Press]]| year =2010| pages =177–178| accessdate =2015-09-01| isbn =1139490508| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=AwcYPAqSp2gC&pg=PA177| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150905084457/https://books.google.com/books?id=AwcYPAqSp2gC&pg=PA177| archive-date =2015-09-05| dead-url =no}}</ref>。
**對於[[耶穌基督後期聖徒教會|耶穌基督後期聖徒教會]]，或[[摩爾門教|摩爾門教]]而言，婚姻之內的性行為是神聖的。摩尔门教教徒認為上帝是为了使夫妻生育兒女以及互相表達愛意，而授予了「性」这件事物给人类。摩尔门教反對教徒進行婚前性行為或對伴侣不忠<ref name="Swatos">{{cite book| author =William H. Swatos| author2 =Peter Kivisto| title =Encyclopedia of Religion and Society| publisher =Rowman Altamira| year =1998| page =464| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =0761989560| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=6TMFoMFe-D8C&pg=PA464| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326125301/https://books.google.com/books?id=6TMFoMFe-D8C&pg=PA464| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref>。
*對於[[犹太教|犹太教]]而言，一個已婚的猶太人需向妻子提供稱為「onah」（依字面意思可解作「她的時間」）的性愉悦。這是名为「ketubah」的猶太婚姻契约的其中一項条件。根據犹太教對婚姻的看法，性慾一般不被認定为罪恶，但需要選取適当的时間、地点以及方式去滿足性慾<ref name="Zilney">{{cite book| author =Laura J. Zilney| author2 =Lisa Anne Zilney| title =Perverts and Predators: The Making of Sexual Offending Laws| publisher =Rowman & Littlefield| year =2009| pages =7–8| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =0742566242| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=Zo-h9D1gqOsC&pg=PA8| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326113614/https://books.google.com/books?id=Zo-h9D1gqOsC&pg=PA8| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref>。
*對於[[伊斯兰教|伊斯兰教]]而言，有婚姻基礎的性行為是一种使人愉悦的靈性活動，以及是一种責任<ref name=columbia/><ref name=islam>{{cite book| author =Abdul Rahman bin Abdul Karim al-Sheha|title=Islamic Perspective of Sex|year=2003|publisher =Saudi Arabia|isbn=9960-43-140-1}}</ref><ref name=islam2>{{cite book| author =Fatima M. D'Oyen|title=The Miracle of Life|year=2007|publisher=Islamic Foundation (UK)|isbn=0-86037-355-X}}</ref>。穆斯林男子可以擁有多達四位妻子。什葉派伊斯兰教允許男子擁有無數段臨時婚姻，這些臨時婚姻短則數分鐘，長則多年。其中該名男子可與跟自己为臨時婚姻关系的伴侣進行性交，但什葉派的女子只可擁有一段婚姻，不論婚姻关系暫時與否。遜尼派女性終生只可結一次婚；不論是臨時的還是永久的婚姻，什葉派女性都只可終生結一次婚。在伊斯蘭教法中，像婚外性行為、通姦、肛交、同性性行為、私通般的性關係皆會歸類為[[齊納_(伊斯蘭教)|齊納]]，並因此而被禁止<ref>{{cite book |last1=Joseph |first1=Suad |last2=Naǧmābādī |first2=Afsāna |title=Encyclopedia of Women and Islamic Cultures: Family, Law and Politics |year=2003 |publisher=BRILL |page=454 |isbn=9789004128187 |url=https://books.google.com.bd/books?id=4Uyypm6T7ZsC&pg=PA454 |access-date=2019-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190512111949/https://books.google.com.bd/books?id=4Uyypm6T7ZsC&pg=PA454 |archive-date=2019-05-12 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=al-Qaradawi |first1=Yusuf |title=The Lawful and the Prohibited in Islam: الحلال والحرام في الإسلام |year=2013 |page=20 |publisher=The Other Press |isbn=9789670526003 |url=https://books.google.com.bd/books?id=iXCNAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA20 |language=en |access-date=2019-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513023105/https://books.google.com.bd/books?id=iXCNAQAAQBAJ&pg=PA20 |archive-date=2019-05-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref><ref>{{cite book |last1=Simon |first1=Rita James |last2=Brooks |first2=Alison |title=Gay and Lesbian Communities the World Over |year=2009 |page=17 |publisher=Rowman & Littlefield |isbn=9780739143643 |url=https://books.google.com.bd/books?id=AGlGTAXlAcsC&pg=PA17 |access-date=2019-04-19 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190513170855/https://books.google.com.bd/books?id=AGlGTAXlAcsC&pg=PA17 |archive-date=2019-05-13 |dead-url=no }}</ref>。
*[[印度教|印度教]]之内對性交有着很多不同的看法，但印度教社會一般認為[[婚外性行為|婚外性行為]]是不道德和可恥的<ref name=columbia>{{cite book|author1=Don S. Browning|author2=Martha Christian Green|author3=John Witte|title=Sex, marriage, and family in world religions|year=2006|publisher=Columbia University Press|isbn=0-231-13116-X|url=https://books.google.com/books?id=qkNE8pRQoboC&pg=PA227|access-date=2017-05-04|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170305181301/https://books.google.com/books?id=qkNE8pRQoboC&pg=PA227|archive-date=2017-03-05|dead-url=no}}</ref>。
*[[佛教|佛教]]的倫理觀念一般認为人不應追求或執著於肉體上的快樂，因為其會把人束缚於生死[[輪迴|輪迴]]之中，也使人們不能達至「[[涅槃|涅槃]]」的境界，由於佛教僧侶（即[[比丘|比丘]]和[[比丘尼|比丘尼]]）要致力於實現這一目標，所以他們会遵從戒律規定，完全禁慾。佛教的其他行為戒律（[[毗奈耶|毗奈耶]]）和經典（[[波羅提木叉|波羅提木叉]]）亦會禁止出家人自慰、带淫念地接觸他人、對不同性別的出家人說話，以及發生其他性行为。佛教人士需遵從[[五戒|五戒]]，其中第三个即为「不邪淫」，亦即避免性行為不端。彼得·哈維（Peter Harvey）指出這個戒律「主要是為了避免因性行為而造成的痛苦。通姦——與他人的妻子發生性行为是最直接違反這戒律的作為，部分是因為該人所表現出的『貪』，另一原因則是對他人造成了傷害……如果一名男子與守護女或他女婦進行性交，那麼他就會違背戒律。顯然，強姦和近亲性交也是違背戒律的<ref name="An Introduction to Buddhist Ethics">{{cite book|last=Harvey|first= Peter|title=An Introduction to Buddhist Ethics: Foundations, Values and Issues|publisher=Cambridge|year=2000|pages=71-74}}</ref>。」佛教的典文並没有对非信者作出任何的規定及建議，比如没有規定其能不能自慰、能否發生同性或異性性行为，以及能否避孕。然而根據佛教的倫理觀念，像強姦般的社会性禁忌也可遭視为干犯了第三条戒律。諸如[[龍樹|龍樹]]般的佛教徒亦就此在他們的著作中作出了不同的說明及建議<ref name="An Introduction to Buddhist Ethics"/>。
*對於[[巴哈伊教|巴哈伊教]]而言，只有丈夫和妻子才可發生性關係<ref>{{cite book|author=Kenneth E. Bowers|title=God Speaks Again: An Introduction to the Baha'i Faith|url=https://archive.org/details/godspeaksagainin2004bowe|year=2004|publisher=Baha'i Publishing|isbn=1-931847-12-6}}</ref>。
*[[一神普救派|一神普救派]]並不会在參與者都同意的性交中設立邊界<ref>{{cite book|author1=John A. Buehrens|author2=Forrest Church|title=A Chosen Faith: An Introduction to Unitarian Universalism|url=https://archive.org/details/chosenfaithintro00bueh_0|year=1998|publisher=Beacon Press|isbn=0-8070-1617-9}}</ref>。
*對於{{link-en|婆羅摩·庫瑪立|Brahma Kumaris}}及{{link-en|毗拉毗達·婆羅摩·庫瑪立|Prajapita Brahma Kumaris}}这兩个宗教而言，慾望是所有邪惡的根源，且比杀人更坏<ref name="Liz_Hodgkinson_Peace">{{cite book | last = Hodgkinson | first = Liz | title = Peace and Purity: The Story of the Brahma Kumaris a Spiritual Revolution | year = 2002 | publisher = HCI | isbn = 1-55874-962-4 | pages = 2–29}}</ref>。信仰者会遭鼓勵保持純潔（獨身），目的是為了和平以及即將到來地上的天国。他們相信一旦天国到來（2500年后），孩子便会经由精神力量創造<ref>{{cite book|last=Babb|first=Lawrence A|year=1987|title=Redemptive Encounters: Three Modern Styles in the Hindu Tradition(Comparative Studies in Religion and Society)|publisher =Oxford University Press|isbn=0-7069-2563-7|quote=Sexual intercourse is unnecessary for reproduction because the souls that enter the world during the first half of the Cycle are in possession of a special yogic power (yog bal) by which they conceive children.}}</ref><ref>{{cite book|last=Barrett|first=David V| year=2001|title=The New Believers|url=https://archive.org/details/newbelieverssurv00barr|publisher =Cassell & Co|pages=[https://archive.org/details/newbelieverssurv00barr/page/265 265]|isbn=0-304-35592-5}}</ref>。
*[[威卡教|威卡教]]信徒的相关看法就如威卡教经典《{{link-en|女神的诫命|Charge of the Goddess}}》中所寫的般：「让欢乐的心中充满对我[女神]的崇拜，因为一切爱与快乐的行为才是属于我的仪式。」此一段似乎在暗示威卡教的女神充許人們自由地探索肉欲和愉悦感。亦段亦已跟《{{link-en|巫士守則|Wiccan Rede}}》的最終格言混合：「威卡教的教規八字真言是，『為所欲為傷人不為』<ref>{{cite book|last=Thompson|first= Lady Gwen|title=''Wiccan-Pagan Potpourri''; |pages=Green Egg, №69|publisher =Ostara |year=1974}}</ref>。」威卡教鼓勵人們對他們的性接触負責，不論其种类<ref>{{cite book|author=Hans Holzer|title=The Truth about Witchcraft|year=1971|publisher =Doubleday|pages=128|isbn=0-09-004860-1}}</ref>。
*[[震教徒|震教徒]]認為性交是所有罪惡的根源，故此他們認为包括已婚夫婦在內，所有人都應禁慾。有鑑於此，震教徒的數量不斷下降：从1840年的6,000名下降至2009年的3名<ref>{{cite news |title=The Last Ones Standing |last=Chase |first=Stacey |date=2006-07-23 |publisher=The Boston Globe |url=http://www.boston.com/news/globe/magazine/articles/2006/07/23/the_last_ones_standing/?page=full |deadurl=no |archiveurl=https://web.archive.org/web/20160803030037/http://archive.boston.com/news/globe/magazine/articles/2006/07/23/the_last_ones_standing/?page=full |archivedate=2016-08-03 |accessdate=2017-05-14 }}</ref>。
*印度靈修大師{{link-en|美赫·巴巴|Meher Baba}}認為：「在結婚生活起始之时，伴侶会因慾望和愛而互相吸引，但是经过一段时间的相互依存后，慾望的元素便会減少，『愛』所佔的比例亦会有所增加。经过這個昇華過程后，慾望最终会讓位给深沉的愛意<ref>{{cite book|last=Baba|first=Meher|year=1995|title=Discourses Myrtle |publisher =Beach: Sheriar Press|pages=109|isbn=9781880619094}}</ref>。」

在某些情況下，兩個人之間的性交合会遭視为背离了宗教法或教義。包括[[天主教會|天主教會]]和[[比丘|大乘佛教]]在內，許多宗教的領袖都会被指望完全禁慾，以使其能在宗教事務上投入更多的关注及忠誠<ref>{{cite book|author=William Skudlarek|title= Demythologizing Celibacy: Practical Wisdom from Christian and Buddhist Monasticism|url=https://archive.org/details/demythologizingc0000skud|year=2008|publisher = Liturgical Press|isbn=0-8146-2947-4}}</ref>。

