在[[動物學|動物學]]中，交配一詞通常是指雄性將精子引进至雌性身体內（特別是引进生殖道）的過程<ref name="Kent"/><ref name="Copulation1"/>。[[蜘蛛|蜘蛛]]有分雌雄。在交配之前，雄性蜘蛛会先结一个细小的网，后在网上射精。然後他將精子儲藏在他{{link-en|须肢|Pedipalp}}的贮精囊裏，由此把精子轉移至雌性的生殖器。那些精子雌性可無限期地存儲在體內<ref name="RFB2004Spiders">{{cite book | author=Ruppert, E.E. | author2=Fox, R.S. | author3=Barnes, R.D. | last-author-amp=yes | title=Invertebrate Zoology | url=https://archive.org/details/isbn_9780030259821 | publisher=Brooks/Cole| edition=7th|isbn=0-03-025982-7| year=2004|pages=[https://archive.org/details/isbn_9780030259821/page/571 571]–584 | chapter=Chelicerata: Araneae}}</ref>。

許多生活在水中的動物都會進行[[體外受精|體外受精]]，而體內受精可能是因「在液体介质中保留[[配子|配子]]」的需要而在[[奥陶纪|奥陶纪晚期]]中演化出來。許多脊椎動物（[[爬行動物|爬行動物]]、一些[[魚類|魚類]]，以及大多數[[鳥類|鳥類]]）的體內受精都是以[[泄殖腔|泄殖腔]]交配的形式進行。而[[哺乳動物|哺乳動物]]的交配則以插入陰道的方式進行。許多原始的脊椎動物会以體外受精進行有性生殖<ref name="Starr">{{cite book| author =Cecie Starr| author2 =Christine Evers| author3 =Lisa Starr| title =Cengage Advantage Books: Biology: A Human Emphasis| publisher =Cengage Learning| year =2010| pages =630–631| accessdate =2010-12-09| isbn =1133170056| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=DdU8AAAAQBAJ&pg=PA631| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20160101133232/https://books.google.com/books?id=DdU8AAAAQBAJ&pg=PA631| archive-date =2016-01-01| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name="Denecke">{{cite book| author =Edward J. Denecke Jr.| title =New York State Grade 8 Intermediate Level Science Test| publisher =Barron's Educational Series| year =2006| page =105| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =0764134337| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=dbF6g4geyfsC&pg=PA105| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326114731/https://books.google.com/books?id=dbF6g4geyfsC&pg=PA105| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref>。

對於原始[[昆蟲|昆蟲]]而言，雄性一般會把精子儲存在底質中，但有些則儲存在特殊的身體結構內。牠們的[[求偶|求偶]]過程則只是誘導雌性將精子放至她的生殖器入口，當中沒有任何實際的交配行为發生<ref name="Yadav">{{cite book| author =M. Yadav| title =Breeding in Insects| publisher =Discovery Publishing House| year =2003| page =59| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =817141737X| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=ZC5obBYtusEC&pg=PA59| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326112403/https://books.google.com/books?id=ZC5obBYtusEC&pg=PA59| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref><ref name="Engelmann">{{cite book| author =Franz Engelmann| title =The Physiology of Insect Reproduction: International Series of Monographs in Pure and Applied Biology: Zoology| publisher =Elsevier| year =2013| pages =58–59| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =1483186539| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=4bXYBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA58| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326122645/https://books.google.com/books?id=4bXYBAAAQBAJ&pg=PA58| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref>。在某些生殖过程跟蜘蛛類似的生物中（比如[[蜻蜓|蜻蜓]]），雄性会把二级生殖结构內的精子從其生殖器開口中移出，然後將其用於授精。蜻蜓的相关结構是一組经修改的背板，其位於腹部第二节<ref name="Leonard">{{cite book| author =Janet Leonard| author2 =Alex Cordoba-Aguilar| title =The Evolution of Primary Sexual Characters in Animals| publisher =[[Oxford_University_Press|Oxford University Press]]| year =2010| page =334| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =0199717036| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=PgtXj5R6OfMC&pg=PA334| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326123934/https://books.google.com/books?id=PgtXj5R6OfMC&pg=PA334| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref>。高等昆蟲的雄性会利用从腹部的末端部分延伸出來的雄蟲陽莖，將精子直接注入雌性的生殖道內，但有時精子会包在稱为[[精包|精包]]的膠囊內<ref name="Gullan">{{cite book| author =P. J. Gullan| author2 =P. S. Cranston| title =The Insects: An Outline of Entomology| publisher =John Wiley & Sons| year =2009| page =124| accessdate =2014-12-09| isbn =1405144572| url =https://books.google.com/books?id=E_6-pGOLUgcC&pg=PA124| archive-url =https://web.archive.org/web/20150326123824/https://books.google.com/books?id=E_6-pGOLUgcC&pg=PA124| archive-date =2015-03-26| dead-url =no}}</ref>。

不論雌性是否處於生殖週期中最有可能發生受精的時間段——發情期，倭黑猩猩、海豚以及黑猩猩也会照樣地从事異性性交，这些物种亦会發生[[動物界的同性性行為|同性性行為]]<ref name="Non-human"/>。在這些物种当中，性交已经演變成具有一定的社會作用<ref name="Diamond"/>，不再只是單單的純生殖性活動<ref name="wunsch2017"/>。
